content: See your favorite intergalactic personalities like never before by gazing at these out of character Star Wars prints. Each print measures 12″ x 16″ and depicts iconic characters like Darth Vader, Boba Fett, and C-3PO lounging in flower filled meadows.

content: This “places I’ve been” scratch off map turns keeping track of all your travels into a fun game. This unassuming grey map of the United States will come to life with brilliant color as you scratch off the various states you’ve visited.

Power up your living room decorum by giving it a geeky touch with the Nintendo 64 coffee table base. Ideal for any old school gamer, this custom base is an exact replica of the 3-dimensional logo for the beloved Nintendo 64 console.

Spice up your look with a little south of the border flair using this taco clutch bag. This vibrantly colored hardened foam purse comes topped with all the fixings and features a hollowed out center perfect for storing all your belongings.

Get a buzz going at snack-time by indulging in a few <del>dozen</del> of these Baileys chocolate Oreo style cookies. Each delectable treat is handmade from imported dark chocolate and comes with a Valrhona-chocolate creme filling spiked with real Baileys liquor.

Create the illusion you’ve grown a pair of beautiful wings overnight with this gorgeous butterfly cloak. Inspired by the monarch butterfly, the cloak features a realistic design and comes fitted with wires along the front of the wings so you can easily flap them around.

Fuel your little one’s creativity and imagination by having them play with this wooden rainbow stacker toy. It is handcrafted from sustainably harvested wood, coated in vibrantly colored non-toxic paint, and can be arranged into either a multicolored tunnel or arch.

Create an enchanting atmosphere when the lights go off with help from this stained glass candle holder. This handmade glass gem sports a lively multicolored mosaic that projects brilliant colors onto the walls when a lit candle is placed inside.

This rainbow fudge is the delicious homemade snack that’ll satisfy both your eyes and palate. It’s made from fresh, natural ingredients and comes in batches of either fifteen or thirty sweet and colorful pieces of rainbow colored white fudge.

Set your monochromatic smartphone apart from the rest with a little natural beauty by placing it inside this dry pressed flowers iPhone case. Each crystal clear case gives you full access to your phone’s features and displays a lovely flower themed motif.

Give the Harry Potter fan in your life something to smile about with this lovely charm bracelet. It sports a classy silver finish that goes great with every color and comes full of small Harry Potter themed charms like a lighting bolt and sorting hat.

Place a fun spin on the way you tell time with help from this digital sundial. Rather than relying on batteries or electronics, it’s mathematically designed to let only certain sun rays pass through it depending on the time of day, allowing it to display the time like a digital clock.

Classic Nintendo game systems don’t die – they evolve! Each re-purposed system is a custom made to function as a full six string guitar with all the working features you’d expect from a traditional face melting electric guitar!

Bring a beloved storybook character to life by dressing up in this red velvet hooded cloak. It’s handmade in Spain from rich non-stretch velvet, measures more than two meters long, and features a deep red hue throughout the entire garment.

Easily add a dash of life and color to your home using one of these vertical succulent gardens. These custom gardens feature a colorful assortment of fresh succulents and can be easily hung on the wall to save space.

Transform foul words into beautiful works of art with this swear words coloring book. This digital book is easy to download and features 20 pages filled with all the classics like “twat waffle”, “cockwobbler”, “shitbag”, and “thundercunt”.

Earn some brownie points with mommy dearest by reminding her who her favorite child is using this “Dear Mom” coffee mug. It’s crafted from ceramic and decorated with a heartfelt and comical message reminding her how lucky she is to have you in her life.

Make bath time more enjoyable for the little ones by lathering them down with this LEGO figure soap bar. The handmade glycerine soap comes with an authentic LEGO action figure lodged at the center and features a delightful orange blossom scent.

Leave your skin feeling rejuvenated and silky smooth by applying this dead sea mineral mud mask cream. Not only will it leave your skin feeling refreshed and tightened – but it will also exfoliate your skin, removing toxins and other impurities.

Blur the lines between the real and digital world by altering your appearance with this DIY polygon face mask. The easy to follow instructions will show you how to turn a plain piece of cardboard into an other-worldly geometric mask.

Give your backspace key a little more extermination power using this Doctor Who Dalek key decal. Designed like the sinister Daleks, the viny decal is easy to adhere and can be customized to your desired size and color.

Become the most feared sea creature on the planet and conquer the cold by dressing up in some Cthulhu winter apparel. It covers your entire head and features an opening beneath the tentacles so you can comfortably breathe, talk, and devour inferior beings.

Make science come alive like never before by growing your own mini ecosystem using this beaker terrarium set. The set includes various sized graduated glass beakers you fill up with dirt and nutrients to give birth to stunning plant life.

Brighten up your cubicle’s drab decor with a little color from this 3D printed rainbow octopus. This multicolored invertebrate is printed from high quality ABS plastic and features vibrant articulated tentacles each measuring 3 inches long.

Amaze friends by turning a seemingly normal jar of peanut butter into a cool smoke bomb using this kit. The potassium nitrate you receive looks exactly like PB – allowing you to discreetly carry smoke bombs almost anywhere you go.

titleEN: Get Me A Stripper Foldout Card
content: Ensure your bridesmaids/groomsmen know exactly what kind of party you’re expecting by dropping a not-so-subtle hint with this “Get Me A Stripper” foldout card. They’re printed on white cardstock and can be customized for a variety of recipients.

Brighten up your days with a small blast from the past by opening up this 90s nostalgia kit. Once you pop open this brightly colored pencil box you will be greeted to an assortment of items like beanie babies, slap bracelets, and pogs.

There’s no better way to show the bearded man in your life that you care for him and his glorious facial hair than with this beard care gift box. Inside the classy wooden cigar box, he’ll find everything from beard wash, balm, oil, a comb, and a handy pair of scissors.

Display your love for the classics in true gamer fashion by hanging this Nintendo controller wall print in your pad. This set of downloadable prints comes with 3 high resolution (300ppi) Jpeg files so you can create cool 11″ x 4″ frames.

Prepare a feast fit for royalty at your next GoT watch party with help from this Game Of Thrones cutting board. This gorgeous solid oak board comes expertly engraved with the show’s logo, your choice of house symbol, and a humorous “dinner is coming” quote.

Rock out with some Adventure Time flair by playing with this handcrafted Vamprire Queen bass axe. The iconic red bass affectionately named “Henchman” is crafted from pine wood and made to look exactly like Marceline the Vampire Queen’s red axe.

Experience the epitome of luxury with this smart self-contained bedroom bed. Apart from a comfy king-size mattress, it offers every amenity imaginable – from champagne holders to built-in tables and an aromatic dispenser system.

Witness one of the universe’s most evil tyrant’s destructive power first hand with this Frieza death ball lamp. The lamp’s base is skillfully crafted from foam while the plasma ball gives off a cool electric purple glow.

Channel your inner swash-buckler during your next bonfire using these campfire sword roasters. Instead of boring wooden sticks, these stainless steel roasters are styled like elegant swords complete with a protective heat shield handle.

Bring the majesty of our planetary neighbors into your bedroom with this solar system pillow set. Each pillow in this twelve piece set measures eighteen inches wide and comes decorated with a vibrant and scientifically accurate image of the planets in our solar system.

Add a dash of decadence to your MacBook without breaking the bank using this marble styled cover. The decal features a realistic looking marble design and comes with a backing that’s easy to apply and even easier to remove!

Make your coffee table pop by creating some eye-catching ambient lighting with this geodesic table light sculpture. Perfect as a centerpiece, the sculpture sits on an elegant hardwood base and emits a stunning white glow from the top half.

Summon the Caped Crusader as if you were commissioner Gordon himself by using this miniature bat signal smartphone light. Simply hold this small attachment to your phone’s flashlight and you’ll be able to project the iconic bat symbol onto any surface.

Take your aquatic animals for a leisurely stroll using this aquarium backpack. This one of a kind tank features a completely see through design and includes padded straps so you can comfortably lug your fishy friends around town.

Show off your love of literature in a fun and creative way by decorating your home with the DIY book stairs lettering. Simply place these custom vinyl decals on your steps painted in different shades to create the illusion of a huge stack of books.

Make your BFF’s special day one to remember by letting them know how much they mean to you with this birthday card. Rather than a cutesy poem or message, the card’s honest and blunt message lists all the real reasons why you love them so much.

Bring a little out of this world flavor to snack time with these solar system cake pops. These colorful and delicious handmade pops come in sets of 18 and are decorated like each of the planets in our solar system – including our bright yellow sun.

Stave off boredom during long trips by entertaining yourself with this travel cribbage board. Inspired by the small pocket games used by soldiers during WWII, this classic game comes wrapped in hand-dyed leather and is secured with an antique brass closure.

titleEN: Star Wars & Harry Potter Wall Decal
content: Reflect your geeky personality on your walls by decorating with this Harry Potter and Star Wars themed wall decal. Made out of high quality vinyl, the decal comes pre-spaced and is meant to look like it’s been hand-painted. Lightsaber and wand sold separately.

Make parenting a little more rewarding by carrying around your little gamer inside this Bowser shell baby carrier cover. This handmade canvas and fleece backpack comes with a functional zippered opening and features adjustable straps to fit any size.

Stay warm by transforming yourself into one of your favorite cartoon characters by wearing one of these geeky hoodies. They are available in a variety of styles, from Pikachu to the Ninja Turtles with a matching shell shaped backpack!

Give your bathroom decor an out of this world touch by laying out a few outer space soap bars. They’re handmade with all natural ingredients including coconut, soybean, and olive oil, and are scented with a blend of patchouli, cedar wood, and orange oils.

Find your way around the mystical land of Hyrule using one of these Legend Of Zelda maps. Inspired by the maps from Ocarina of Time and Majora’s Mask, each map is printed on thick paper and aged for added authenticity.

Spice up your living room’s decor by giving it some gamer flair with this Halo energy sword lamp. Skillfully made from laser cut and polished acrylic, the lamp stands at 22 inches when fully assembled, and the sword can be removed from its base for swordplay.

Add color and life to any part of your home using this monogrammed letter planter. Each planter is custom painted to your specifications, come filled with a multitude of vibrant succulents, and is also capable of being hung on the wall.

Bring a small piece of Hyrule into your backyard by decorating with these Legend Of Zelda ceramic pots. Each hand thrown pot is customized to look just like the ones from Ocarina Of Time, and they even feature an item inside should you decide to smash them.

Add some quaint ambient lighting to any part of your humble abode using this recycled vintage bulb oil lamp. This eco-friendly lamp sports a sturdy wick that’s easy to light and sits on an elegant wooden base so you can place it on virtually any flat surface.

Make lunchtime your children’s favorite time of the day by packing their meals into these Mr. & Mrs Little Bread Slice lunchboxes. These cute and cuddly lunchboxes measure nearly eight inches around and are lined with thermal fabric to keep food fresh.

Brighten up your little one’s wardrobe with a bit of whimsy using this dinosaur cowl pattern. The pattern is easy to follow and can be crafted using any chunky yarn, meaning that you can combine colors for endless possibilities.

Soar higher than cloud nine when you take a hit from this beautiful celestial space glass pipe. This lovely piece is hand blown from thick, high quality glass and decorated with an eye-catching motif designed to mimic our vast cosmos.

Class up your look without sacrificing technology with help from this Apple Watch vintage leather strap. Each elegant genuine leather strap comes with a quality stainless steel buckle for a secure fit and is available in a range of sizes.

Increase your bedroom’s groovy factor with some ambient lighting from this 3D printed mushroom lava lamp. Each unique lamp is printed from high quality ABS plastic, comes in various vibrant shades, and stands at 8.5″ tall making it ideal for any desktop.

Go from fashionista to warrior at the drop of a dime by wearing this ninja hoodie scarf. This unisex accessory measures 42 inches long from the top of the head and comes with a stretchy black fabric you can easily pull up to conceal your face.

Bring your favorite post-apocalyptic game to life by slipping inside this Fallout T-51 costume. Inspired by the iconic armor from the video game, it’s masterfully decorated to create a battle-hardened look and is made from lightweight materials to facilitate movement.

Make any bland outfit come alive – literally – by accenting it with living succulent jewelry. From bracelets to necklaces to earrings, each eye-catching piece in this earthy collection features a lively arrangement of real succulent plants.

Add some Middle-earth flair to your look using these silver dwarven hair beads. Each metal bead is crafted with a singular pattern and is designed to stay in place for days without damaging your hair. Now all you need is a fine axe!

Put your taste buds on overdrive next time you’re craving some sweets by biting into these chocolate cherry cheesecake brownies. The brownies are handmade from fresh, natural ingredients and come in batches weighing over one pound.

Show off your love for sweets by accenting your bathroom’s decor with these donut soap bars. These glycerin soaps come in sets of four brightly colored and scrumptious looking mini donuts with a delightful sweet fragrance no one can resist.

Take your Batman cosplay to the next level using this Batman Arkham Knight helmet. It’s expertly crafted from fiberglass resin, polycarbonate, and hardened plastic – and features LED eyes along with an internal fan to prevent fogging.

Protect your desktop from water damage by resting your drinks on these floppy disk coasters. These handmade coasters feature actual floppy disks encased in vinyl, and finished off with a cork base to prevent sliding on sleek surfaces.

Spice up your bathroom’s decor by giving it an exotic look using this Moroccan tile wall decal. These vinyl decals are easy to apply and feature gorgeous and vibrant color schemes that make them ideal to use in any bathroom or kitchen.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Neon Nail Polish
content: Now you can brighten up your look using this glow in the dark neon nail polish. This easily applied custom shade – known as freckles – has small neon colored dots that come alive when placed under some UV lighting.

Use the power of the Dark Side to help keep your favorite plant blossoming. This geeky planter is handcrafted using sealed concrete in the form of the iconic weaponized space station and is small enough to easily fit on any desktop.

Make coffee time more relaxing by reminding yourself to stay cool with this “keep calm” stencil. Simply place the stencil over the coffee and pour your favorite topping – like cinnamon – to create a perfectly written message.

Earn serious style points this winter by knitting yourself a pair of these unique Converse socks. After downloading the digital pattern, simply choose your favorite color yarn and follow the steps to craft yourself a one of a kind pair of kicks.

Let your blunt and comical sense of humor shine through while doing your part for the environment by carrying around your produce in this “Groceries & Shit” tote bag. It’s made from heavy-duty canvas and comes with two strong shoulder straps for easy transport.

Bring your favorite video game character to life by incorporating this Buster sword to your costume. Modeled after the iconic weapon from Final Fantasy VII, this 72″ sword is made with game-accurate details and is light enough for anyone to wield.

See what life is like for Pokemon when they’re not battling by checking out this pokeball diorama. Each pokeball comes with a transparent cover so you can peek inside and see a Pokemon like Vaporean or Ninetales in their natural habitat.

Turn any room in your home into a private makeup station with help from this vanity mirror LED kit. The string of ultra bright LEDs comes with an adhesive backing that you can stick on in seconds without using any tools.

Make your party stand out from the rest by giving guests their invitations in these cassette tape gift card holders. Simply download and print the PDF, then cut, glue, and fold to create these brightly colored cassette tapes.

Celebrate the career of Hollywood’s greatest thespian like a true fan with one of these Bill Murray character paintings. Each print depicts The Murray in a scene from one of his iconic movies like Caddyshack, Ghostbusters, and The Life Aquatic With Steve Zissou.

Bring the magic of the Big Apple to your home office with this glowing New York City desk. This work of art depicts the majesty of this enormous city with stunning detail – giving you a birds eye view of everything in the city that never sleeps.

Declare your bedroom a magic-friendly environment where everyone is accepted – even muggles – with this Wizards Welcome sign. This Harry Potter themed sign comes with a handy self-leveling hanger and is printed using the iconic font with lighting bolts in the lettering.

Look stylish while you tote your fancy DSLR around by attaching it to this camera scarf strap. The strap is handmade from a soft and delicate fabric, and is available in a variety of trendy and vibrant designs so you can match them to any outfit.

Assure that the adventurer in your life can always find their way back home with a personalized engraved compass. The compass features a timeless brass frame and comes engraved with your choice of message and font style.

Place a spooky twist on snack time by serving up a batch of these chocolate skull truffles. These shockingly sweet creations are available in a variety of savory flavors and come filled with delicious fillings like caramel, peanut butter, and hazelnut.

Gain a deeper understanding of your favorite caffeinated beverage by sipping it from this chemistry molecules coffee mug. This clear glass mug’s educational motif displays all the molecules that go into your prime roast.

Make coloring time a little more educational for the kids with these chemistry element crayon labels. Instead of displaying regular colors on the labels, they come printed with the names of the chemicals that actually make up the color of the crayon.

Receive an extra jolt of energy in the mornings by showering with this caffeinated mocha latte soap. A soothing combination of dark cocoa, coffee, and caffeine restrict blood vessels and minimize redness while helping to reduce fine lines and wrinkles.

Make your MacBook the envy of every comic fanboy in town by slapping this comic book keyboard cover on it. It’s made from vinyl and depicts a different superhero symbol from both the Marvel and DC universes  on each key.

Give your home a whimsical touch guaranteed to spark up conversation with guests by bringing in an upholstered faux taxidermy piece. Each unique piece in this stunning collection depicts a majestic fabric animal in remarkable color and detail.

Let your felines experience the joys of the greatest game ever made by getting them this Super Mario Bros. cat complex. It mounts vertically onto the wall and features a hollowed out structure connected by two green warp tunnels.

Watch instructional videos and read recipes with ease while cooking by placing your device on this kitchen tablet and smartphone holder. The holder fits most kitchen cabinets without hindering door movement and features an adjustable upper clamp.

titleEN: Damn It Feels Good To Be A Gangsta
content: Make your humble abode a bit more homely without losing your street cred by crafting your own “Damn It Feels Good To Be A Gansta” stitch. The downloadable pattern perfectly pairs vintage 1980s sampler kits with lyrics from the iconic Geto Boys song.

Bring a small piece of your favorite arcade game to life by decorating your game room with this Space Invaders rug. This handmade four foot wide rug is available in 8 distinct color combinations, so you can easily match it to the color scheme in your home.

titleEN: Together Since His And Hers Shirts
content: Put your love on display for the whole world to see by walking side by side in these “together since” his and hers shirts. Each pair of shirts are customizable in color scheme, size, and personalized lettering, so you can create a perfect matching outfit for you and bae.

One-up your local barista with your own vulgar creations using these rude coffee stencils. Simply place the stencil over the mug and sprinkle your favorite powder to create eye-catching images of middle fingers, curse words, and male genitalia.

Give your garden a striking feature that’ll capture anyone’s attention by planting these heirloom deep purple rose seeds. They germinate in about 40 days and grow with a distinct purple/maroon hue that give them a near black appearance.

Bring a touch of nature into your work environment by saving your data on this realistic stone USB drive. This unique accessory is handcrafted from polymer clay to provide an authentic appearance and can be purchased in either a 8GB or 16GB model.

Showcase mother nature’s beauty wherever you go with this delightful real flower pendant necklace. This tiny terrarium displays a gorgeous arrangement of dried flowers alongside plants and moss that are encased in an protective glass bell jar.

Shield your eyes from external light while you slumber by wearing this sleep mask pillow. Available in a variety of designs such as a winky face or sleepy face, the pillow makes your head look like you have two giant drowsy eyes.

Keep the little ones safe from creatures that go bump in the night by placing these Pokemon night lights on the job. They’re available in several Pokemon character designs and feature a remote control multicolored LED so you can customize the glow.

Bring an air of sophistication and elegance to tea time by infusing your drink using this scrotum tea bag holder. It’s hand crocheted from acrylic yarn and fitted with a rope at the top so you can keep the contents from spilling out when tea bagging your mug.

Instantly create a starry sky in any room by turning on this clay light sconce. The egg shaped sconce projects a fun lighting pattern onto the walls and comes with a flexible stainless steel arm that allows you to position it however you want.

Add a brilliant dose of color to any outfit by accessorizing it with this fire opal necklace. The lovely glass pendant hangs on an elegant silver plated necklace and displays an array of vivid colors clashing with one another.

Keep your collection of geeky literature organized and propped up in an eye catching manner using these Star Wars AT-AT bookends. Crafted from solid wood, they’re engraved with fine detailing and are meticulously assembled by hand to ensure quality.

titleEN: Light Up League Of Legends Crystals
content: Bring your favorite champion to life by lighting up your room with one of these League Of Legends crystals. Each brilliantly cut crystal sits on an elegant base and contains an embedded LED that brings the laser engraving to life.

Show our neighboring planets some love by giving your outfit some cosmic flair with this solar system planets ring. Each ring is cast in silver and adorned with a small handmade pendant depicting all the planets in our solar system.

titleEN: Co-Workers I Want To Punch Notebook
content: Take a detour off the high road and succumb to your petty ways by keeping track of everyone who’s ever crossed you with help from this discreet notebook. It sports an elegant black buckrum cover and provides enough space to fit your growing list of enemies.

Document your life’s most memorable events in true Whovian style by writing them down in this Doctor Who TARDIS journal. This handmade journal features a sturdy cardboard cover designed to look like the Doctor’s iconic space and time traveling machine.

Turn a fun project into Junior’s favorite place to rest by crafting him a comfy hanging cloth crib. This simple DIY project shows you how to make a sturdy hammock-like crib that your infant will love rocking in all day long.

Make your cinephile buddies green with envy by bringing home this swimming Alien prop. This stunning statue is masterfully hand sculpted from a rigid rubber using incredible detailing that stretches over 12 feet long – making it the ideal centerpiece for any room.

Bring everyone’s favorite merc with a mouth to life by dressing up in this Deadpool replica motorcycle suit. Styled exactly like Deadpool’s signature ensemble, this all leather suit will protect you from road rash and give you a license to mess with anyone you want.

Have the kids set sail for fun and adventure by surprising them with this wooden ship treehouse. This elaborately themed treehouse is handmade with superb attention to detail and features 130 square feet of actual deck space.

Get your hands springtime clean by rubbing them in dog shit. This novelty dog poop shaped soap is handmade from natural ingredients that won’t harm the skin and has surprisingly pleasant fragrance despite its outward appearance.

Give your outfit a stunning a nerdy touch by accenting it with this lovely solar system planet necklace. The necklace features a vintage brass coating and comes with two sided pendants displaying our solar system’s most beautiful planets in vivid color.

Earth’s mightiest warrior has come to save you from the darkness in the form of this Goku kamehameha lamp. This handmade lamp features the legendary Saiyan hero shooting an enormous kamehameha wave that provides some ambient lighting.

Give your poker games a George R.R. Martin twist with these Game Of Thrones playing cards. Each face card of this hand illustrated deck features the series’ main characters like Robb Stark and Jon Snow and are decorated with a map of Westeros on the back.

Give any room a touch of gamer flair by bringing in this NES controller coffee table. This geeky piece of furniture is painted to look like a giant version of the classic NES controller and is covered with a protective polyurethane layer.

Give your contemporary home a bit of old world charm with this vintage light bulbs chandelier. This work of art features a multicolor salvaged wood board base along with sixty vintage bulbs hanging at various heights that combine for a stunning glow.

Get your tired body feeling like new again by dropping an achy muscles bath bomb in your bathtub. It’s made with carefully selected essential oils and natural ingredients to provide a top quality aromatherapy bathing experience.

Transform your backyard into the coolest hangout spot ever with one of these custom built treehouses. They’re expertly built from solid wood and designed around the tree’s existing structure, guaranteeing no two are alike.

Become the living embodiment of Titus by suiting up in this life size space marine costume. This custom made UVA foam suit covers you from head to toe in thick armor that’s decorated to look just like a space marine from Warhammer 40K.

Bring some style into your home office with this rustic reclaimed wood desk. Available in a variety of elegant finishes, each desk is handmade from reclaimed wood and accented with distinguished and sturdy mid century steel legs.

Drink your brew with a little old world charm by sipping if out of one these medieval oak mugs. The mugs are handcrafted from solid wood and finished off with a sturdy stainless steel handle for a secure and comfy grip while you drink.

Give your two-wheeled ride a little nighttime flair by accenting it using these LED bicycle wheel lights. Each light is made to fit most adult sized bikes and gives off a bright neon glow designed to increase your visibility with style.

Get an extra jolt of energy from your sugary treats by snaking on these coffee bean cookies. Each savory cookie comes garnished with a mix of chocolate chips and dark roast coffee beans that make this the perfect treat for coffee lovers and dessert lovers alike.

Turn yourself into a delicious sugary snack by making cookies of your beautiful mug using these custom portrait cookie cutters. After submitting your photo, you’ll be sent a 3D printed mold of your face so you can stamp it on some fresh dough.

Secure your spot as parent of the year by surprising your little hell raisers with this cabin treehouse. This mammoth hangout spot  is handmade from solid wood and accented with everything from a climbing wall, slide, and even a smoke stack chimney.

Set your mass produced laptop apart from the rest by giving it a playful touch using this spacebar space decal. The rectangular sticker is handmade from vinyl and displays four colorful planets from our solar system surrounded by a flurry of stars.

Bring an air of whimsy to any room in your home by lighting up this faerie magick candle. Sprinkled with glitter and topped with colorful dripping wax accents, the candle is designed to burn for 45 hours while release an intoxicating aroma.

Real roses are so cliché. Get your honey something she’ll actually appreciate by purchasing a lovely bouquet of these piranha plants! Inspired from the classic Super Mario Bros series – it’s sure to be the centerpiece in any room.

Step your texting game up by creating a personalized emoji of yourself. Simply submit a photo of your lovely mug and you’ll receive a custom image in both .jpg and .png format that you can then use to bombard friends and family with while texting.

Give any room in your home an extra inviting atmosphere by lighting up this cereal scented candle. This handmade soy wax candle comes with a cotton wick inside an elegant glass jar and features a delightful Cap’n Crunch aroma.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Pool Table
content: Give your man cave a futuristic feel by lighting the room up with this glow in the dark pool table. This 7 foot table can be customized with your choice of colored felt and comes outfitted with bright light strips that give the table a cool futuristic glow.

Increase your odds of making whoopee by buttering up your sweetie with one of these red velvet whoopie pies. These delectable treats are baked with all-natural organic ingredients and come filled with soft velvety cream cheese icing.

Bring your little crime fighter’s favorite comic to life by transforming their bed into a Batmobile. Using this downloadable PDF and a bit of elbow grease, you’ll be able to completely change you child’s standard twin bed into a bitchin’ Batmobile.

titleEN: Put A Ring On It Mug
content: Belittle your single friends, family, and co-workers by flaunting around your happiness using this this personalized engagement mug. The printed message will spread the joyous news while not so subtly directing the eyes to that fat rock.

Instantly spice up any plain outfit with a little color by slipping into these tie dye rainbow Converse. These classic high tops provide a comfy fit and are expertly dyed by hand, ensuring that no two pairs are the same.

Turn fantasy into reality by giving your partner this Valentine’s Day naughty coupon booklet. This downloadable PDF gives you all the tools necessary to construct a fourteen coupon booklet you and your lover can customize with all your perverted desires.

Ensure your delicate smartphone remains protected and always at hand by placing it inside this steampunk iPhone case bracer. Handmade from steel, brass, and leather, this unique case allows you to wear your phone like a piece of jewelry.

titleEN: Take Off Your Pants Valentine’s Card
content: Skip the games and romantic banter and get straight to the good stuff by giving your sweetie this “Take Off Your Pants” valentine’s card. It humorously tweaks the classic “roses are red, violets are blue” poem so your significant other knows what’s in store.

Experience first hand what out world actually looks and feels like by hanging up this scientifically accurate 3D topographic relief carving. Crafted from crack resistant kiln dried Canadian Maple, the carving displays our world’s terrain with impeccable detail.

Spark up like a true Pokemaster by sliding your trusty Bic into one of these Pokemon lighter sleeves. Each handmade hard sleeve is designed to look exactly like a classic Pokemon card that’s sure to make you the envy of all your geeky friends.

Navigate through the treacherous land of <del>Hyrule</del> suburbia using this Navi fairy replica light. Handmade from resin, each lamp features an embedded LED that can be changed to 1 of 6 vibrant colors – and it fits in the palm of your hand.

Indulge your eyes as well as your taste buds by feasting on these rainbow Rice Krispies treats. Each batch is handmade from scratch and comes professionally packaged to ensure freshness in every single bite.

Show your significant other how much they mean to you with the modern times Valentine’s Day card. Sonnets, poetry, and love songs are simply too outdated. This novelty card contains a message your sweetheart will love – and most likely will post on Instagram.

Disconnect from the modern world and get in touch with mother nature by spending a night in this treehouse tent. With running electricity, a comfy bed, and a working bathroom, this luxurious treetop abode is sure to make your night in nature unforgettable.

Bring the galaxy’s most lethal bounty hunter to your city by dressing up in this Super Metroid Varia suit. It’s expertly crafted from lightweight materials to facilitate movement – making it the ideal costume for any convention.

Skip the games and let your Valentine know how you really feel about them with these custom chocolate messages. They’re handmade from creamy milk chocolate and are skillfully decorated with any message you’d like – no matter how crude or kinky.

You smart. You very smart. We da best. You a genius. I appreciate you. You loyal.  This DJ Khaled Valentine’s card features the big buy himself with his heart in his hands so your sweetheart knows that with him/her by your side, you can always win win win no matter what.

Keep your cat from scratching up your furniture in true gamer fashion using this Pac-Man cat complex. It installs directly onto the wall to save space and features graphics designed to look like a level from the iconic arcade game.

Go from rags to riches without needing a fairy godmother by slipping into this beautiful Cinderella dress. Based on the dress from the live action movie, this gorgeous blue gown can be customized to your exact measurements for a perfect fit.

Give your baked goods a signature designer touch with help from one of these custom pattern rolling pins. They come engraved with intricate and beautiful designs that stamp onto the surface of the dough as you run the pins across.

Keep the outdoor festivities going longer even on cold winter nights by gathering everyone around the fire pit picnic table. The table features a narrow gas powered fire pit running along the center so everyone seated gets a piece of the hot firey action.

Brighten up your garden in true Pokemon master fashion with these lovely little Bulbasaur planters. These 3D printed planters comes shaped like the famous little grass type Pokemon with a hollowed out back so you can cultivate a variety of plants.

Combine your love of literature and gaming into a stylish package that will add flavor to your room using this Super Mario Bros. shelf. This sturdy shelf is crafted from hardwood and styled to look exactly like the coin boxes from the classic video game.

Show your sweetheart that your love for her will never die by giving her these gorgeous metallic roses. Made from sturdy sheet metal, they’re expertly crafted into beautiful roses and given a vibrant paint job that will last a lifetime.

Tell your beloved she’s the one in true Whovian fashion by popping the question with the Doctor Who TARDIS engagement ring. The double band comes studded with diamonds and showcases a small blue sapphire studded TARDIS in the center.

Keep your kitty in shape and entertained by installing this cat exercise wheel in your humble abode. Designed to be mounted onto the wall for maximum space efficiency, it will help keep your cat in tip top mental and physical condition.

Turn your next shindig into an event no one will ever forget by installing an inflatable LED photo booth. The inflatable design makes it easy to transport, it can be set up with one of sixteen fun colors, and is big enough to accommodate up to ten people at once.

Command the audience’s attention when you hit the stage dressed in this peacock dancer costume. This handmade beauty transforms you into a majestic and vibrantly colored peacock that is guaranteed to leave everyone’s jaw on the floor.

Give yourself one more reason to bum out on the couch all day by elevating your comfort level with the sofa arm rest table. The table fits right over the arm rest to provide you with a convenient little table you can use to rest your phone, drink, or snacks on.

Give your backyard a prehistoric feel by unleashing the metal T-Rex sculpture. Unlike the original giant lizard, this sculpture presents the legendary predator in a slightly smaller scale, making it ideal for displaying in a variety of locations.

Make dinner time something worth looking forward to by spicing up your bland cooking with some sriracha sea salt. Perfect for using as a rub before cooking or as a finishing salt with your meal, it will give your food a much needed kick of flavor.

Take Comic Con by storm when you show up decked out in this custom made Halo Master Chief Spartan armor suit. The suit is intricately detailed from head to toe and can be customized with a specific paint job upon request.

Let that special someone know she’s the one you choose by giving her a lovely bouquet of colored pokeball roses. Each rose is meticulously decorated by hand to look like a lovely blossoming pokeball – making this the ideal gift for any geeky girl.

Turn the most fattening of dishes into guilt-free treats by eating them with the “Calories Don’t Count On This Spoon” utensil. Rather than stress over your caloric intake, simply follow the spoon’s message and dig in – your future self will thank you.

Make your room look like a magical forest by providing some accent lighting with the glowing mushroom night light. The tops of the mushrooms illuminate to provide a natural soft glow that gives the room a truly mesmerizing appearance.

Give your culinary creations an exotic dash of flavor with help from the shiitake mushroom growing kit. Known for its unrivaled taste and texture, the kit gives you everything you need to grow this living organism right on your kitchen counter.

Plant the seeds for your children’s fear of the ocean by bathing them in a tub clogged by the shark tub drain stopper. With a design inspired by every child’s worst nightmare, it’s designed to appear as if a blood thirsty shark has sprung out from the drain.

Tote your gear around in true Whovian fashion with this nifty TARDIS backpack. This eye-catching felt backpack comes styled like the Doctor’s iconic time travelling TARDIS – providing you with ample space to store all your stuff.

Bigfoot sightings won’t be such a rare occurrence anymore when you’ve got this Sasquatch shaped cookie cutter in your kitchen. Available in four different sizes, these sturdy plastic cookie cutters are perfect for baking up some edible missing links.

Give your young crime fighter the bed he deserves, but doesn’t need when you purchase this Batman themed bed. This custom made bed is shaped to look like the caped crusader’s iconic Batmobile and is accented with bat symbols on the wheels and along the frame.

Put on the most crowd-pleasing show this side of the galaxy by taking the stage with the C-3PO guitar. This protocol droid has been re-purposed and outfitted with features like a Behringer neck and oak beams so you can give an out of this world performance.

Show everyone there’s nothing sexier than a symmetrical smile by accessorizing with the braces ring. If you’re a fan of orthodontics, or have an eye for the quirky and kind of creepy, this unique ring of pearly whites will be right up your alley.

Provide some relief from the brutal cold like a Nordic warrior by lighting up this viking ship fire pit. This viking themed fire pit features a menacing black sail, two rows of ores for added authenticity, and just like the viking boats of its day – it’s built to last.

Help your offspring on their quest for greatness with these children’s superhero costumes. These handmade costumes include a heirloom quality winged cap and double sided cape that’ll fit your little ones perfectly as their imaginations soar.

Reward yourself for sticking with a healthy habit by keeping your H20 in one of these etched glass water bottles. This unique water bottle helps reduce plastic bottle waste and comes designed with a hand etched nature themed image.

Put your travel exploits on display for all to see by decorating your room with the world travel peel off map. Each time you visit a distant land, you can come back home and peel off the corresponding black layer, revealing your latest expedition.

Keep your cash and other personal belongings at hand in an aquatic manner by storing them inside this octopus purse. Each time you need to grab something, you simply pop open the clasp and dig through the octopus’s vacant body.

Create life giving fire in true warrior fashion by setting the weapons of the Svenhaellin fire pit ablaze. The mighty axe and sword are thrust through the shield and come lined with gas valves along the handles so that the weapons themselves are the source of fire.

Maximize your chances of making contact with the other side by conducting your seance using this hand sculpted Ouija board. The board is custom built from fir wood and is coated in natural oils and pine resin for maximum quality and durability.

Turn your schoolyard promise into a binding legal contract with these pinky promise temporary tattoos. The tattoo goes on with absolutely no pain and lasts for a couple of days or until you break your promise – whichever comes first.

Give your outfit a cute geeky touch by keeping your hair in place using these Super Mario themed bobby pins. Each bobby pin comes adorned with either a small Mario hat or Princess Peach crown handcrafted from polymer clay.

Make your room look like an old haunted pirate vessel by outfitting it with these octopus light switch plates. The plates are skillfully painted with a vintage nautical motif and are designed to fit any standard double toggle light switch.

Provide morbidly colorful accent lighting to your room by turning on one of these skull lamps. Cast using a special rotomolding process for added strength and durability – they’re ideal for Halloween parties, seances, and other fun filled satanic rituals.

Roleplay an alternate universe by wearing one of these industrial cyberpunk cosplay costumes. Available in a variety of eye catching designs, these extremely detailed custom made outfits will transform your puny body into that of a menacing cyberpunk.

Add hours of fun to your outdoor party with these beautiful oversized wooden dice. Each set of dice is crafted from fine Douglas Fir – delivered in a burlap sack for easy transportation so you can bring the good times with you wherever you go.

Help your young aviator keep their bedroom organized by using this Red Baron airplane shelving system. The vintage design is made from fully welded metal and modeled after the Baron’s iconic World War I era fighter plane.

Familiarize your young artist with the tools of trade by letting them color using the crayon tattoo machine. This novelty crayon holder comes in a variety of vibrant hues and is perfect for a child curious about mommy’s White Snake tattoos.

Bombard your senses with a double blow of color and flavor when you bite into a rainbow birthday cake. This delectable homemade treat comes stacked with seven delicious and vibrant layers of vanilla cake smothered in creamy white icing.

Show your house guests what happens when they overstay their welcome by proudly displaying this morbid chandelier made from human bones. Every macabre lighting fixture is shaped using humeri, femurs, skulls, spinal columns, and pelvises.

Avoid loneliness by crafting your own little army of lovable Minions using this amigurumi pattern. The pattern is easy to follow and includes detailed instructions in addition to an abundant supply of helpful images.

Accessorize your outfit in true skater fashion with one of these lovely recycled skateboard deck rings. Each ring is handmade from a seven layered maple skateboard deck and is sanded down by hand to a smooth finish that brings the multi-colored wood to life.

titleEN: Jurassic Park Shaving Cream Can Prop

Release the Kraken in your bathroom when you install this tentacle toilet paper roll holder. This skillfully handcrafted tentacle is made from sturdy resin and is coated with acrylic paint to give it an antiquated bronze finish.

Join the Dark Side and never again worry about your wine going stale using these Star Wars wine stoppers. Each stopper is made from a distinct metal and can be customized with your choice of iconic characters like Darth Vader and Boba Fett.

Transform old sweaters and clothes into whimsically styled garments by following this fairy coat instructional guide. This fun and informative PDF shows you everything you need to know in order to create vibrantly colored coats.

Transform yourself into a ruthless post-apocalyptic gang leader using this Mad Max Immortan Joe mask. The mask is expertly sculpted by hand – covering  half your face – and looks just like Immortan Joe’s metallic skull respirator.

Bring a small piece of Halloweentown into your home by lighting up your bedroom with this Jack Skellington night light. With the flick of a switch the Pumpkin King himself comes to life – keeping the kids safe from Oogie Boogie as they slumber.

Step aside Lisa Frank – there’s a new must have journal in town. Each artistic 3D clay journal features an intricately themed cover depicting various wild animals such as frogs, elephants, owls, and even dragons in stunning detail.

Outshine everyone around you by stepping out in these light up sneakers. Available in both men’s and women’s sizes, each pair features an insanely bright LED sole that’s rechargeable and offers over 8 hours of glow time – making them ideal for music festivals.

Ensure your gamer spouse pays attention to the new bundle of joy in your lives by dressing him/her up in this Nintendo Game Boy onesie. This geeky garment will make your tiny tot look like an adorable and cuddly version of the classic portable gaming device.

Give your outfit a touch of flair as unique as yourself by accessorizing with one of these personalized signature necklaces. This fun little piece is entirely cast in sterling silver and is available in either a polished or matte finish.

Heat up this side of the galaxy by dressing up in this provocative Star Wars R2-D2 latex bodysuit. This hand crafted piece features an eye-catching Star Wars inspired design that transforms your fleshy body into a voluptuous droid.

Become the center of attention by drawing all eyes on you with these glow in the dark heels. After being charged under a UV light, this dazzling pair of shoes emits a bright glow that make these a must have staple for any serious clubber or party-goer.

titleEN: I Didn’t Get You Shit Card
content: Give the gift of honesty to your loved ones by keeping it real with the “I Didn’t Get You Shit” card. Rather than lie about why you didn’t buy that special someone a thoughtful gift, the blunt message printed on this card will help keep expectations to a minimum.

titleEN: Lord Of The Rings Ringwraith Costume
content: Strike fear in the hearts of everyone on the streets – and Middle Earth – when you head out dressed in the Lord Of The Rings Ringwraith costume. This professionally made costume has been stained and treated to achieve maximum authenticity.

Carry the majesty of the cosmos on your wrist by accenting your outfit with this stunning galaxy space bracelet. This handmade item comes adorned with small pendants that each feature a vivid design depicting galaxies and planets in our universe.

Class up the walls of your <del>parent’s basement</del> bachelor pad like a true gamer with these high-class game paintings. Each masterpiece elegantly depicts a scene or theme from a beloved game like the Legend Of Zelda or Super Mario Bros.

Take your favorite tunes to the farthest reaches of our galaxy by playing them on the Star Wars AT-AT boombox. This geeky boombox has been masterfully outfitted with an intricately designed AT-AT casing that seamlessly blends modern tech with sci-fi.

Provide shelter for your kitty like any self respecting gamer would by offering him this chain chomp cat bed. Modeled after one of Mario’s deadliest foes, it provides a comfortable place for Mr. Whiskers while doubling as an excellent addition to any game room.

Transform your puny human feet into majestic eye catching hooves by stepping into a pair of rhino hoof boots. The intrepid design comes cast around the boot so that you can comfortably walk around while creating the illusion that your feet are hooves.

Show off that lovely radiant smile even if you don’t have one yourself – by sporting the dentures ring. This quirky piece comes styled like a small pair of pearly white dentures that you can match with any outfit to give your look some eye-catching flair.

It’s dangerous to go alone – take this Zelda Master Sword! This handmade item is expertly crafted from polyurethane foam and hand painted to replicate the iconic video game sword – making it a must have collectible for any Zelda aficionado.

Perform the most sinister prank known to aviation by inserting these helpful Fight Club inspired flight safety pamphlets into your plane’s seats. The prints feature exquisite art work any film buff can appreciate while displaying terrifying emergency flight procedures.

Combine your love of technology and entomology by decorating your home office using these circuit board bugs. These customized creepy crawlers are handmade using spare circuit boards to resemble a variety of real life insects.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Temporary Tattoos
content: Give your Burning Man outfit some extra flare by accenting your look with these glow in the dark temporary tattoos. Available in various abstract and captivating designs, they glow bright green when in the dark, making them ideal for drug-laden music festivals.

titleEN: Dragon Ball Z Goku Dog Costume
content: Transform your beloved pooch into Earth’s mightiest hero by dressing him up in this Dragon Ball Z Goku costume. Designed for small dogs, it features Goku’s iconic Turtle Hermit symbol on the back and even comes with a pint size power pole.

titleEN: Life Size TARDIS Police Call Box

Give your children brutal nightmares by decorating their playroom using this realistic Super Mario piranha plant. Inspired from the classic game, this gruesome plant comes to life in a way you never thought possible – making it a must have for any gamer’s art collection.

Experience the same joy the Mother of Dragons feels when you take home your very own set of Game of Thrones dragon eggs. Inspired by the acclaimed series, these handmade eggs are meticulously crafted and painted to resemble the real thing.

Put the finishing touches on your technicolor music festival getup with these brilliant LED arm guards. They can be adjusted to your arm’s width and are powered by lithium-ion batteries so you can light up the party for hours on end.

Create deliciously blasphemous meals with help from these Genesis oven gloves. Styled to look like the hands of Adam and God at the moment of creation, these cotton oven gloves provide a comfortable fit as you prepare your divine creations in the kitchen.

Become the center of attention at the next Comic-Con with your wise-cracking humor while wearing the Deadpool cosplay morphsuit. Made from athletic grade material for a superb fit, it comes with everything you need to turn yourself into everyone’s favorite anti-hero.

Place the finishing touches on your Dark Knight ensemble by complementing it with this Batman utility belt. If you’re looking for quality and realism, this handmade item comes fully detailed and expertly painted to look just like the real thing.

The “Level Up” gamer birthday card is the ultimate way to wish your Player #2 another year of life. This novelty card is printed on high quality stock paper and provides a clever way to wish that gamer buddy a happy birthday.

Relax after a long day of battling Rebel scum by plopping down on the Stormtrooper wooden lawn chair. This handmade furniture features all wood construction and superb artistic detailing to achieve a realistic look making it ideal for any Empire loyalist.

Negotiate the most romantic makeout session of your life by drawing up the terms and conditions with the makeout session contract card. You and your sweetie will be able to hammer out all the details so both of you go in knowing full well what to expect.

Give your rock and mineral collection a dose of brilliant color with the addition of the watermelon tourmaneline gemstone. This exotic and food-like gemstone comes in thinly cut slices that showcase the vivid green and pink hues at the center.

Unleash the Dovahkiin warrior within by donning this Skyrim viking helmet. Based on the classic helmet from the video game, it’s expertly painted to achieve a realistic appearance and made from lightweight materials so you can wear it comfortably.

Turn heads as you show your favorite team some love by wearing a light up sports hat. These custom made hats comes in a variety of color schemes/team styles and feature bright neon trimming that outline the logo so it’s visible to everyone in the room.

Give your game room an eye-catching centerpiece when you decorate it using the Borderlands clap trap replica. It’s skillfully made with the highest level of detail and expertly painted in the classic Hyperion yellow just like in the video game.

Make your next party truly unforgettable as you burst everyone’s eardrums with the giant alien monster sound system. This out of this world sound system stands at seven feet tall and is capable of emitting enough sound for a small concert.

Overload your taste buds with these chocolate cheesecake truffles. Your mouth will be treated to a creamy explosion of flavor unlike you’ve ever experienced from the moment you bite into one of these chocolaty balls.

Begin a promising career in the paranormal by hunting down ghouls using the Ghostbusters ghost trap and pedal. This meticulously detailed prop is ideal for use in live action roleplaying and includes everything you and your team will need when the ghosts arrive.

Have your pets/livestock enjoy the great outdoors without fear of attack from nearby wildlife by keeping them inside the outdoor geodesic dome. Measuring twenty feet in diameter, the dome functions as an ideal aviary or animal pen for small pets and poultry.

Be the envy of every hipster within a five mile radius by listening to your favorite bands through the iPhone vintage speaker horn. This distinguished and battery-free speaker amplifies your iPhone’s sound while adding a hint of old school flair to the room.

Say your prayers and count your blessings with these Golden Girls prayer candles. Your favorite senior citizen gal pals are back dressed in their finest robes and ready to listen to your woes while helping make your prayers come true.

Unleash the hell hounds of Hollywood upon your living room with this Ghostbusters terror dog statue. The fierce demon dogs from the original Ghostbusters flick are recreated with incredible detail and stand at six inches tall making them ideal for the coffee table.
