Give your home’s entrance a cool macabre vibe as you create some eerie mood lighting courtesy of the skull wall sconce. These brilliant sconces are made from recycled vodka bottles and work great for lighting your home during the Halloween season.

Tie the knot like a true Whovian when you walk down the isle holding the Doctor Who sonic screwdriver. This one of a kind bouquet boasts lovely origami styled white and navy blue roses skillfully crafted from book pages topped off with a sonic screwdriver handle.

Don’t just give her your heart, throw in a few eyeballs and assorted body parts when you surprise her with the zombie Valentine’s Day felt candy. Unlike traditional sweets which eventually expire, these rotten pieces stay in perfect condition forever – like your love for her.

Keep your delicious little angel looking irresistible to everyone by keeping her warm in the burrito baby blanket. This fleece blanket is topped off with cheese, lettuce, tomato, and works great as a creative Halloween costume or for everyday use.

Stay ahead of the fashion curve by embracing the trends of the future by wearing the chrome cyborg corset. This handmade corset comes fully decked out with a robotic inspired motif ideal for putting together the quintessential sci-fi outfit.

Give some real value to your money as you fill up your wallet with these cartoon superhero dollar bills. Rather than look at Washington’s stern mug all day long, you’ll be treated to a vivid and comical rendition of some of your favorite cartoons.

Channel the essence of the swingin’ sixties and make your outfit pop with the tie dye psychedelic socks. The vibrant design on these high socks is so groovy and far out that they may just trigger a flashback if you look at them long enough.

Proclaim yourself queen of the dance floor when you show up wearing the eye catching metallic Cleopatra wig. The chic wig sports a classic Cleopatra hairstyle formed from insanely bright chrome strands that’ll turn you into the focus point of any room.

The iconic portable gaming device we all grew up on has received a vintage makeover with this rustic retro Game Boy. The classic Game Boy Pocket has received a custom paint job that makes it look like an antique from a past century.

Get the fiesta started on a colorful note by customizing your guests’s cocktails using colored margarita salt. Apart from making it easy to keep track of your drink, these vibrantly hued salts come in specialized tins to allow you to prepare them without making a mess.

Put a positive spin on the “D” grade by inking a barely passing student’s paper with a Danny Devito stamp. This hand carved wooden stamp comes with a custom image of Danny Devito’s beautiful mug that will cushion the blow of receiving an awful grade.

Sow the seeds of the coming apocalypse by growing your own undead with the zombie planter garden starter kit. This hand made work of art is masterfully sculpted with loads of realistic and gory details to create a life-like display.

Get one step closer to fulfilling your childhood fantasy of morphing into an action hero with the Power Rangers helmet. Expertly cast in resin, the helmet perfectly captures every detail of the now iconic original series Power Rangers.

Stop waiting for expensive limited edition pieces for your ever-growing toy collection and opt for these handmade LEGO figurines. Whether you’re in the market for tertiary Simpsons characters or lesser known superheroes, this shop has them all.

Shut up and take my rupees! This deluxe cold cast polyurethane reinforced with fiberglass shield is fashioned after the Skyward Sword style with life like scale and a convex shape for a realistic appearance – making it ideal for cosplayers.

The magic of springtime is never far away when you accessorize with the dandelion globe ring. Made with exotic dandelions handpicked from the coast of Ireland, this handmade gem is the perfect wearable accessory for a a nice Sunday afternoon stroll.

Let your little tike’s imagination soar when you let them fulfill their fantasies with these children’s superhero capes. No matter what super-powered being they idolize, there’s a pint-sized cape waiting to join them on countless crime fighting adventures.

Remind your beloved that marriage is until the bitter end with this stunning diamond skull engagement ring. This elegantly morbid piece of jewelry features a double sided skull holding up a crown halo of diamonds to symbolize your eternal union.

titleEN: Batman Slap Meme Dry Erase Board
content: Now you and your friends can make up countless creative scenarios and keep the laughs coming all day long as you watch the Caped Crusader slap that little bitch ass Robin for his idiotic remarks with the Batman slap meme dry erase board.

Nothing burns as long as human flesh, that’s just science. Next time the power goes out, these human face candles will keep your home lit up for hours on end while treating you to an unforgettable face-melting performance.

Guard the greatest secrets in Hyrule – or your budding social life – safely by writing them in the Zelda Triforce journal. This handmade journal sports a distinguished leather cover and is accented with a classy Triforce image any Zelda fan will love.

The miniature petting zoo is open for business thanks to these tiny crochet animals. These impossibly cute little critters span the entire animal kingdom from domestic animals like dogs and cats to more exotic species like the elusive narwhal.

He may be useless as a Pokemon but as a fashion accessory you won’t find a better choice than Magikarp. This hand crocheted Pokemon hat displays all his fishy glory – just pray he doesn’t decide to evolve while you’re wearing him on your head.

Transform your little bundle of joy into an adorable little henchman by dressing him in the crocheted baby minion costume. Handcrafted with love in every stitch, it features a vivid blue bottom complemented by a brightly colored beanie in the form of a minion head.

Mr. Vincent Vega and Jules Winnefield are back from the dead – sort of – and ready to do your bidding. With hair that’ll put Elvis to shame, these <del>bad motherfuckers</del> Pulp Fiction taxidermy rats come dressed in their finest suits whilst packing heat.

Have some fun with your growing baby bump by sporting this peeking baby maternity shirt. Available in a variety of colors and both genders, the creative design shows your unborn fetus peeking their little head from the zip-fastener in your stomach.

titleEN: Star Wars AT-AT Walker Ear Plugs
content: Straight from the frozen battlefields of Hoth, the Star Wars AT-AT walker ear plugs have made their way to our Earth to provide some geeky flair for your outfit. Perfect for the oppressive Imperialist, these stainless steel plugs are made to order in various sizes.

Craft a one of a kind costume that’ll astonish and terrify by topping it off with one of these paper mache animal masks. The expertly crafted masks comes accented with pieces of hair and fur for added realism, in both a male and female form.

Vanquish your junk mail and credit card statements with one fell swoop of the Zelda Master Sword letter opener. This double edged letter opener has been expertly crafted to resemble the sword from Ocarina of Time and features its own stone base.

Get into the holiday spirit without actually having to wear a hideous holiday garment by baking up a batch of ugly Christmas sweater cookies. Baked with love in every kitschy sweater pattern, these Christmas treats are the perfect companion to a hot cup of cocoa.

Ring in the festival of lights in prehistoric style with the T-Rex Hanukkah Menorah. While your more religiously conservative family members might scoff at you, this golden ‘Manorasaurus Rex’ will make the holiday season one to remember.

Who’d ever thought having your foot chomped on by a great white could feel so good? Once this handmade shark sock latches its yarn teeth around you and envelops your feet in its cozy innards, you’ll never want him to let go.

Place a touch of magic in any room with the Harry Potter 3D wall letters. The letters come designed in the classic Potter font seen plastered across each book cover and also feature the classic jagged lightning accents to provide a truly authentic look.

The octopus necklace – also know as the jewel of the deep – is a handcrafted piece so stunning it’s fit for underwater royalty. This completely customizable necklace features an intricate design of colorful octopus tentacles that complement any look.

Prove you’re the ultimate G.O.T fan by ‘inking’ your body with a Game Of Thrones temporary tattoos. This detailed piece goes on with minimal pain and proudly displays the Stark family’s signature words surrounded by details pertaining to their adventures.

Let the world know you and your sweetheart are officially off the market by branding each other with the personalized stacking rings. If there’s a special someone you always want with you, these stylized rings are ideal – and a lot less permanent than tattoos.

Make those long work hours go by faster by entertaining yourself with the iridescence of the bismuth crystal. Each crystal features its own unique blend of colors while featuring a low melting point that allows you to alter the crystal’s physical appearance.

Channel your spirit party animal while raising the roof with the rainbow light up bear hood. You’ll light up the dance floor the moment you walk in and the ultra bright LEDs built into the faux fur begin lighting up in brilliant colors and patterns.

Bring some whimsy into the stuffy I.T. office environment by decorating your cubicle with some internet masterpieces. What better way to capture the essence of the internet than a gun-totting ninja kitty riding a fire-breathing unicorn with laser vision.

Take your origami skills to frightening heights by learning how to craft a cardboard skull mask. The easy to follow instructions provide a step by step guideline to transform a regular piece of paper or cardboard into a spooky skeleton mask.

Summon the benevolent beast of the deep whenever you desire a little candlelit company with the Godzilla shadow caster. When placed next to a candle, this pint sized reptile casts a larger than life shadow to create the illusion the legendary Godzilla has arrived.

Use furniture to play your favorite Nintendo games by decorating your room with the functional NES controller coffee table. This handmade gem gives the room a unique retro feel while allowing you to actually hook it up to your NES for unparalleled levels of gameplay.

Add a touch of whimsy to your room’s decor with the Beauty and the Beast clock. Styled after the Beast’s tightly wound  butler, Cogsworth, this jubilant wooden clock makes an ideal peace for brightening up your children’s room.

Get your little princess into cosplay from an early age by transforming her into video game royalty with the Princess Zelda crochet costume. This darling ensemble is hand tailored and can be worn by children ranging from ages 2-4.

Give the game room some great ambient lighting with the LEGO Super Mario Bros lamp. This retro LEGO lamp features an old school 8-bit graphic depicting the famous Italian plumbers heroically chasing after a mushroom and flower on their quest to power up.

Enlist the aid of the world’s best cook by prepping your meals using the Heisenberg cutting board. This one of a kind kitchen accessory is made using durable bamboo wood and comes decorated with an image of Walter White’s iconic alter ego on the board’s surface.

Commemorate the coolest President ever to <del>get serviced</del> serve with the epic Bill Clinton poster. This contemporary masterpiece depicts our 42nd President kicking ass and taking names all while looking like a rockstar.

Give the children some irreparable psychological damage by having them sleep with the Pinhead doll. This Hellraiser inspired doll comes skillfully decorated like a miniature version of the dreaded hell spawn leader of the Cenobites.

Butch up any room in your home by accenting it with the comfy boxing glove bean bag chair. Styled like an old-school leather boxing glove, this ginormous bean bag makes the perfect place for any boxing enthusiast to relax and unwind after a rigorous sparring session.

Satisfy your craving for <del>brains</del> sweets by taking a big chomp out of a zombie sugar cookie. These custom treats are baked fresh to order and come decorated like brain-thirsty zombies complete with blood, scars and a ton of sugar – yum!

Compliment your costume party with the perfect spooky treats by serving up some psychedelic chocolate skulls. These creepy treats are shaped like miniature skulls with half their cranium cut off exposing their savory and sugary braaaaaaains.

Lord Of The Rings fans look no further than the Hobbit bag for the ultimate way to store all your geeky gear. This hand carved and painted leather bag features a design inspired by the round door at Bag End complete with Gandalf’s Rune.

Give some new life to one of your favorite gaming devices by lighting the room up with the Nintendo console lamp. This geeky light source utilizes the classic NES console and its controllers to create a fixture that any gamer would approve of.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Soda Bottles
content: Create a lively nighttime environment at the old homestead simply by using some glow in the dark soda bottles for some mood lighting. The glass soda bottles are styled like the classic coke bottles of yesteryear and emit a vibrant glow perfect for parties.

Prepare for the apocalypse by practicing your zombie slaying skills on the zombie pinata. Designed to look like a terrifying zombie, Mr. Chompie comes dressed in a dashing shirt and jean combo that he accents with a stylish noose so you can beat him while he hangs.

Power up your bedroom with the equally comfortable and geektastic retro Nintendo bed set.  Inspired by the original 1980s Nintendo gaming machine, this geeky bedspread morphs your traditional bed into a giant old school multiplayer console.

If you’re the type that loves poking the eyes out of people in pictures, you’ll go nuts for the creepy baby doll head lights. These re-purposed doll heads emit an eerily soothing glow ideal for creating a hauntingly pleasant environment at your next  Halloween party.

Top your morning cup of Joe with some humor by stirring it with the coffee drinker’s spoon. This vintage piece of silverware comes custom stamped with a short comical phrase designed to brighten up those drab weekday mornings.

Experience the finer things in life by digging into one of these gourmet seven layer s’mores. Roasted and infused with real smoke, these handcrafted treats are the ultimate sinful snack while you lounge around by an open fire.

Become the envy of the office by transforming your workstation into an awe inspiring light show with the light up cube. This compact cube emits a bevy of wonderful and vivid hues that can be customized to match your style or mood.

Reminisce over your greatest defeats and triumphs in gaming history as you sip your cup of Joe from the Nintendo Game Boy coffee mug. With a retro design depicting a heart stopping Pokemon battle, it’s the ideal way for any gamer to get their day started.

Fallout fans will now be able to own their very own Pip-Boy 3000. This stunningly detailed prop features a lightweight Styrofoam design, covered with wood putty and acrylic paint to achieve a realistic appearance – just don’t count on it to provide any useful information.

Accent your outfit with the wings scarf and create the illusion you’ve sprouted a pair of glorious wings overnight. The majestic feather wing design on the scarf is accented by a stunning vintage green backdrop great for complementing a variety of looks.

Pay homage to your favorite horror flick mass murderer with the Jason hockey mask spoon. Ideal for the deranged cereal killer in your family, this quirky item features Jason’s iconic hockey mask skillfully sculpted onto the back of the spoon.

This Halloween season, give into your Dark Side and hit the streets wearing the Star Wars Darth Revan costume. This handmade costume includes a detailed mask, flexible form-fitting torso armor – sensitivity to the Force sold separately.

Embody the most fearsome villain in the city by dressing up in the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Shredder helmet. It features the iconic blade shaped helmet design in addition to a custom mouth guard to complete the look of the dreaded Shredder.

Give your room a macabre ambiance with the skull chair. Designed to look like a human skull, the chair features a realistic wrap-around graphic and comes with a movable jaw piece that lifts up to reveal a comfy and cozy resting spot.

Conquer the open skies in a way you never thought possible by strapping on a pair of mechanical wings. These high-tech wings come with brilliant LED lighting accents at the tips and can extend to four and a half feet wide with the flick of a switch.

Get the piece of mind you deserve by entrusting your home’s security to the metal RoboCop statue. At a commanding 8’2″, this fully metallic work of art looms over your yard and stands in a menacing pose to quickly deter any would be intruders from your home.

Immortalize yourself in your dorkiest of fantasies by placing yourself in your favorite games, cartoons, and movies with the personalized geeky portraits. At last, you’ll finally see what you would look like with pointy elf ears or battling on some far off alien planet.

Transform yourself into a fun loving fairy with the Tinkerbell costume wig. When paired with a pixie styled green dress and a pair of darling fairy wings, the only thing you’ll be missing from this is the magical fairy dust.

Complete the look of Pallet town’s most famous trainer with the Pokemon Ash cosplay costume. Equipped with Ash’s signature green fingerless gloves and iconic red and white baseball cap you’ll have everything you need to begin your journey – Pikachu sold separately.

Look fiercer than ever by accessorizing with the predator claw rings. While the intriguing style does little to help in the love department, the unique design transforms your dainty fingers into deadly weapons no one will want to mess with.

Spend some quality time with the Autobots by adding the giant Transformer to your backyard’s landscape. This colossal statue stands at nearly six and a half feet tall and features a powerful and intricately designed body made from recycled materials.

Treat your fellow ravers to a wild light show on your face by wearing the rainbow light up sunglasses. Made using the classic and always fashionable Wayfarer model, they come outfitted with brightly colored neon lights that run along the entire frame.

Achieve inner peace while adding a touch color to your home’s decor with the red maple bonsai tree kit. The life giving kit comes with everything necessary to grow your very own miniature tree – making it an ideal gift for any member of the family.

Brighten up everyone’s night when you show up wearing these chic light up cowgirl boots. This custom made pair of boots come outfitted with dozens of tiny lights that shine bright and will get you noticed wherever you go. Yeehaw!

Proclaim yourself the fairest maiden at the party when you show up dressed in the Snow White vinyl costume. This handmade ensemble is tailored for the perfect fit, accented with vivid colors and intricate detailing to help you pull off the look of this gorgeous maiden.

Get ready to raid Pandora and take Comic-Con by storm when you show up in the Avatar amp suit costume. The outfit transforms your puny body into a mechanized weapon of destruction designed to strike fear in the hearts of all indigenous life forms.

Bask in the warm glow of decomposing flesh by lighting up some melting zombie candles. Nothing sets the mood quite like snuggling with your significant other, lighting a zombie’s head on fire and watching him melt away over the course of several hours.

He said NO to drugs, brought Gorbachev and the sinister U.S.S.R. down to their knees, and invented Reaganomics. Now you can show your patriotism by commemorating the greatness of the 40th president with the Ronald Reagan riding a velociraptor painting.

Scare the costumes off trick-or-treaters that approach your home with help from the Venus flytrap Halloween decoration. Unlike their smaller cousins, these mutant sized Venus flytraps are equipped with gigantic razor sharp teeth and a monstrous protruding tongue.

Take your costume to infinity and beyond when you show up dressed in this amazingly detailed Buzz Lightyear getup. With features like a custom space helmet and deployed wings on the back, you’ll look like an exact replica of the iconic toy and movie character.

Morph into your favorite crime fighting reptile as you stay warm with the Ninja Turtles hoodie. This custom made hoodie provides a comfortable loose fit and is accented with professionally sewn fleece appliques to complete the look of these mutant turtles.

Rocket off to dreamland in comfort and style on the galaxy bed covers. These handmade satin covers feature a dazzling image of the universe printed onto the surface of the comforter and pillow cases so that you’re surrounded by the cosmos as you slumber.

Think of the Harry Potter iPhone case as a stylish patronus that guards your phone against scratches instead of Dementors. Made in the likeness of the famed wizard, the case features his classic specks, lighting shaped scar and his stylish Gryffindor scarf.

Provide a little flair for any dull room by hanging the stained glass dragon suncatcher. This handmade sculpture – inspired by winged beasts from Game of Thrones – projects incredible visual effects onto the walls as sunlight passes through it.

Leave your competition speechless and wow the audience by performing your routine in the crystalized leotard. This bejeweled garment provides a comfortable fit while its bright and sparking accents ensure you remain the center of attention.

Wreak havoc across <del>Termina</del> your home town by channeling the powerful dark magic of the wearable Zelda Majora’s mask. This handmade item is an exact replica of the mask from the game and features fabric tie straps and foam blocks for a comfortable fit.

Glitter switchplate covers are the ideal way to give your plain home a <del>tasteless</del> fabulous makeover without breaking the bank. Every inch of these custom switchplates feature a luxurious glitter coating designed to turn them into the focal point of any room.

titleEN: Crazy Cat Lady Family Car Sticker
content: Show the world how much you love your feline family with the crazy cat lady family car sticker. This handmade vinyl sticker is available in various vibrant colors so that you can proudly show off your ever growing clowder of kitty cats in a comical way.

Keep your arrows organized while looking the part of a medieval warrior by storing them inside the archeress leather quiver. This custom quiver features intricate brass accents and comes with a leather strap so you can comfortably carry the quiver on your back.

While you wouldn’t want to color with them, these are definitely the crayons you’ve been looking for. Each crayon features a hand-carved miniature sculpture of classic Star Wars characters like C-3P0, R2-D2, and Lord Vader himself.

Become your city’s very own symbol of hope by donning the Batman Dark Knight costume. This amazingly detailed costume is hand tailored and boasts all the body armor and accessories necessary to convincingly pull off the caped crusader look. I’M BATMAN.

titleEN: Home Is Where The Weed At
content: Nothing says home sweet home like plopping down on the sofa, lighting one up and admiring the “Home Is Where The Weed At” sign. This quaint embroidery is handmade with <del>THC</del> TLC in every stitch and adds to the homey environment of the house.

Your favorite Hylian characters have crossed over into unfamiliar lands and its left them a bit pixelated. The Legend of Zelda Minecraft figurines take these beloved characters and gives them an awesome 8-bit makeover using brightly colored beads.

Give your tiny rodent the gift of flight when you outfit him with the steampunk winged guinea pig armor. This custom armor is designed to comfortably fit your guinea pig while a pair of graceful leather and brass wings majestically spread above.

titleEN: Super Mario Bros Brick Planter Box
content: Give your garden a power-up with the Super Mario Bros brick planter box. The planter features a wood burned question mark symbol and brick wall design that wraps around the entire planter, making it an ideal place for gamers to grow their own magic mushrooms.

I am Groot, I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot. I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot, I am Groot – I am Groot I am Groot – I am Groot. I am Groot I am Groot; I am Groot I am Groot, I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot!

While it may not offer much protection, the Zelda Hylian shield pillow delivers the comfort you crave after a stressful day of smashing pots and rummaging for rupees. Handmade in the image of Link’s iconic shield, it’s ideal for any gamer’s bedroom.

Achieve inner piece from the comfort of home with the ancient Buddha Zen garden terrarium. This Buddha sits in the middle of a peaceful garden overrun by growing vegetation that together creates a tranquil setting for you to meditate in front of.

Turn that pile of useless hoarded crap into a beautiful work of art with this personalized skull sculpture made from your own belongings! You can send just about anything lying around the house from old watches to trinkets, and have it used in the creation of the skull.

Ensure your day has a 99.9% rate of good luck by keeping the Heisenberg Buddha figurine by your side. This pudgy figurine encompasses the best from both worlds – balancing Heinsenberg’s aggressive ambition with the Buddha’s patience and wisdom.

As the overlord of the house, your cat expects nothing but the best and you must abide by his wishes for fresh drinking water by installing this water drinking fountain. No opposable thumbs required – your cat only needs to stand up on two paws to reach the fresh water.

Provide A-1 catering for Malibu Stacy’s next soiree by ensuring the staff serve mini clay food. These miniature entrees are handmade and expertly decorated to resemble real food. It’s guaranteed to take your daughter’s playtime to the next level.

When your <del>power level</del> RPM is over 9000 – handle it like a Super Saiyan with the Dragon Ball Z shift knob. A perfect addition for the car of any anime fan, it replaces your boring old shift knob with Goku’s iconic four star Dragon Ball.

Accessorize your feet when going sans footwear with the ivory barefoot sandals. These custom made sandals are skillfully woven from organic cotton and fit comfortably whether you decide to wear them with or without shoes.

Join the prestigious ranks of the Green Lantern the moment you put on this sterling silver Green Lantern replica ring. This handmade collector’s item displays the iconic lantern symbol and can be fully customized with either yellow gold, white gold or silver.

Indulge your unresolved childhood issues while spicing up your love life riding atop the BDSM rocking horse. Built to handle all types of erotic punishment, she waits patiently for you to jump on and ride her back and forth as hard you as can for as long as you can!

Make your child’s playroom a bit more incredible with the LEGO head wall clock. This jolly LEGO man always has a smile on his face as he informs you of the current time while simultaneously adding some unique playfulness to the rooms decor.

Take a fashion tip from the caped crusader and opt for all black accessories such as the Batman hair bow. With its unique bat shaped contour, the hair bow works perfectly for placing a little bit of Bruce Wayne flare onto your outfit.

Host an orgy of relaxation in your backyard when you install the mega hammock! This gargantuan hammock – at what point is this not classified as a tarp? – is custom made out of a tough bonded nylon thread and is built to handle several people all at once.

Bring a little piece of the wizard world into your boring old muggle life with the Harry Potter themed Monopoly. The special edition Monopoly game comes in a distinguished wooden chest and is filled with all the magical characters and places from the series.

Unleash a fun mini celebration with a single quick release of the push-pop confetti. Upon pushing the stick at the base, an explosion of multi-colored confetti is shot into the air – making it an ideal item for celebrations of all kinds.

Hang out with the father of Gonzo journalism any time you want with the Hunter S. Thompson finger puppet. Equipped with his signature hat, vest, cigarette holder, and aviator shades, he’s ready for whatever drug and booze infused adventure you have in store.

It’s a common sight in any urban sprawl, but we guarantee you’ve never seen a shoe toss quite like this lamp. Inspired by the ubiquitous landmark, the lamp dangles off a telephone pole while lighting up the room with halogen bulbs inside the shoe.

Brighten up your day when you light up your carny food with the light up cotton candy sticks. These handmade treats – ideal for parties – offer a fun and eye-catching alternative to traditional lighting that children and drug addicts will love.

Pay homage to your favorite show as you protect your smartphone with the Iron Throne iPhone case. Inspired by the imposing throne of the king, the case comes with a gritty color scheme and protruding swords that’ll make you rethink placing it in your pockets.

Keep your hands toasty in true super hero fashion when you cozy up to the Iron Man crochet wristwarmers. With a custom design that pays homage to Tony Stark’s iconic suit, you’ll remain warm and fashionable all day long with this geeky accessory.

How terrifying would your childhood have been if you were told that the tooth fairy was a psychotic serial killer? Using legally acquired real human molars, the tooth fairy necklace is a truly morbid interpretation of the fabled fantasy figure who visits you while you sleep.

Flip the script on your favorite villains by tearing them to pieces – literally – with the horror icon jigsaw puzzles. Once completed, each puzzle displays a stunningly horrific portrait of each villain that any horror movie buff would love.

Start your incredible journey off on the right foot by exchanging vows using the Millennium Falcon ring. These geeky wedding bands come in a variety of equally opulent finishes that any Star Wars fan will absolutely love.

It’s about time you added some character to your home’s decor using the Doctor Who electrical outlet sticker. These removable vinyl matte decal anthropomorphizes your electrical outlets into tiny versions of our favorite Time Lord.

Spice up your outfit by toting around your personal items in the taco purse. Modeled after a crunchy hard shell taco, this hand made compact purse comes with all your favorite fixings and is topped off with a heaping helping of shredded cheese.

All the way from the awesome ’80s, those devious Gremlins are back and are now yours to own! For lovers of cheesy ’80s flicks, the life sized Gremlins are a dream come true. Each Gremlin is masterfully sculpted to recreate the monstrous little guys.

The King might sit on the Iron Throne, but the Queen can look even more fabulous by wearing the Iron Throne shoes! These heels come cleverly decked out with dozens of tiny plastic food pick swords spray painted to resemble the Iron Throne, in shoe form.

Instill fear in your fellow gamers with a roll of the dragon dice. These customized dice come decorated with an intricate dragon design painted skillfully to make the dragon practically come to life with every single roll.

Make a bold statement in your humble abode with the porcupine quill mirror. A bona fide conversation piece, this handmade mirror boasts a stunning porcupine quill design running a sharp course around the entire frame.

Rest your weary body like a true Pokemon master after you swap out your bed for the Snorlax bed. Better than any king size bed on the market, this handmade Snorlax bed utilizes the superfluous blubber to provide a cozy sleeping spot.

Relive your greatest childhood gaming adventures as you shower with the Nintendo 64 cartridge soap. Each bar of soap is shaped like a life size replica of the most famous N64 cartridges we all spent a good chunk of our adolescent life devoted to.

Enjoy the company of the Pumpkin King himself as you chow down your breakfast with the Jack Skellington cereal bowl. Breakfast will be that much more enjoyable for fans of the classic Tim Burton flick when they’re eating out of Jack Skellington’s skull.

Relive your favorite episodes of the hit 90s show with the Friends apartment paper diorama. This handmade gem perfectly captures Monica’s iconic apartment right down to her yellow cleaning gloves and Phoebe’s dollhouse – could this BE anymore awesome?!

Upgrade your puny human body and become the hero you’ve always dreamed with the Iron Man Arc Reactor. This handmade replica is made with such craftsmanship that it’s sure to be the crown jewel in your vast collection of Marvel memorabilia.

Hey girl, looking for the perfect pair of panties? Introducing Ryan Gosling’s face panties. Made out of boyfriend material, it’s the closest you’ll get to sitting on Ryan Gosling’s perfectly formed face. It’s one pair of panties that won’t be dropping anytime soon.

Unleash your inner Jedi and fight off the Dark Side with the Star Wars lightsaber replica in your capable hands. Made from a resilient aircraft grade aluminum, this handmade item is the closest you’ll get to ever owning a real lightsaber.

Bring honor to your family by having the best dressed doggy on the block with the samurai dog costume. This hand made leather custom makes your canine friend look like a feared and respected samurai that all other pets will bow down to while he sniffs their asses.

Look dapper in the classroom with this utterly nostalgic composition notebook tie. The composition notebook’s globally recognizable two tone design makes it the perfect gift for a teacher, principal, or unnoticed genius janitor with a troubled past.

Melt faces off in less than 12 parsecs when you commandeer the Millennium Falcon bass guitar. Upon seeing you take to the stage with an illuminated Millennium Falcon, all the intergalactic groupies will be fighting over you instead of the lead singer.

Decorate your home with a true treasure from the sea – the glass octopus. Hand crafted from glass and borosilicate, this stunning creation come draped in vibrant and creative styles ideal for complimenting any plain home decor.

Be the envy of all Westeros when you adorn this beautiful purple wedding style necklace. This surprisingly potent jewelry was crafted in the likeness of the piece worn by Sansa Stark – and it’s definitely to die for!

Let the easy day/rough day wine glass help take the edge off with the perfect dosage of wine. Thanks to the wine glass’s clever design, you’ll always know the exact amount of wine needed to relax you after a long and hectic day.

Show your geeky significant other that you want them as your life long co-pilot with the Star Wars X-Wing ring. This masterfully crafted ring combines black and white diamonds along with rubies to create an elegant piece of jewelry that any Rebel scum would love.

Blast your hunger into oblivion with delectable Mega Man cookies made from this specialized cutter. The Mega Man cookie cutter comes shaped like an 8-bit outline of your favorite blue robot character that you can decorate as far as your artistic skills take you.

Make poker nights more cunning by playing with the Game of Thrones playing cards. This custom designed deck is a real treat for all fans of the show. Each suit represents a different house while the cards display your favorite characters in amazing detail.

Keep up with Joneses by transforming your home into a classic Mario level with the Super Mario Bros flag. The flag bears the iconic shape and design of the iconic 8-bit flags at the end of each level and makes an ideal gift for any gamer.

Become a member of the deceased with this line of custom “Living Dead” full body costumes. This full outfit is ripe with detail, offering multiple bloodstain shades and rotting ripped clothes that will bring any Halloween or zombie themed costume party “to life”.

Take a small piece of your favorite Disney flick wherever you go with the Up movie balloon necklace. This small pendant is shaped like the iconic Up house and includes a plethora of brightly colored balloons to help your outfit pop with color.

As the old saying goes, “if you liked it you should have put a giant cathedral ring on it”. More than just a ring, it’s wearable art – a sculpture for the hand that sticks out 50mm in the air as it displays the ominous structure of darkness.

Tie the knot in overwhelming geeky fashion with this Star Wars inspired Tie Fighter ring. This stunning custom made ring is forged from your choice of gold, silver, or platinum, and is accented by the a jaw-dropping one karat black diamond in the center.

When traditional spectacles just won’t suffice, take a cue from Ichabod Crane with the steampunk Sleepy Hollow goggles. This distinguished pair of goggles comes equipped with more lenses than you’ll know what do to with, and are excellent for cosplaying.

Scare intruders off your land with the “Trespassers Will Be Eaten By Zombies” sign displayed prominently on your property. Anyone even thinking about going near your abode will go running back the way they came to avoid becoming a zombie happy meal.

content: Place a touch of surrealism to any room in the home with the glow in the dark chandelier decal. The decal depicts an extravagant chandelier you can stick virtually anywhere you want and enjoy the magical ambient lighting it provides once fully charged.

Before you head out into the streets to fight crime or hit on nubile news reporters, make sure you’re bundled up with the Ninja Turtle hats. Each hand-knit yarn beanie turns the top of your noggin into your favorite hero in a half shell complete the signature colors.

Say no to uninvited apparitions in your home with the Ghostbusters coffee table. This geeky custom made table will tie together your living room while serving a double purpose of sending a clear message that ghosts will be busted in your home.

It’s a jungle out there, even in your own backyard. The hippopotamus lawn ornament is the fun way to transform your dull yard into a more wild and exciting place to be. It measures 22″ long and is made from concrete which makes it ideal for outdoor use.

Witness the Lord of the North of Grassteros in all his glory. He sits on the Throne of a Thousand Shovels in King’s Lawnding. The gnome realm is in disarray and there are rumors of gnome zombies from Cannibal Rock. Prepare yourselves, summer is coming.

The rainbow wig is the fun and vibrant hair accessory that’ll fit virtually any outfit your wear. From formal to casual to Halloween costumes, no matter what color scheme you decide to go with, you’ll find a color to match on the rainbow wig.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Elvish Dog Collar
content: Get your unruly dog under control with the one collar to rule them all – the glow in the dark elvish dog collar. This geektastic dog collar is made from vegetable tanned leather and comes with the iconic elvish inscription engraved into it that also glows in the dark.

Who needs coffee in the morning when you can scare yourself awake? These grotesquely designed mugs – hideous as they may look – are made with a stunning level of artistry for a one of a kind mug no one else will mistake for their own at the office.

Save important documents in true Victorian fashion with the steampunk glowing USB drive. This 16 gig drive is designed with a distinctive steampunk body and features an embedded crystal that glows bright blue when transferring your data.

Take a part of your beloved spouse wherever you go with the fingerprint wedding band. Forged of beautiful white gold, this unique wedding band comes engraved with your significant other’s fingerprint so that no matter where life takes you, they’ll always be with you.

Transform your wine collection into a creative alcohol filled prehistoric display with the Stegosaurus wine rack. The creative design of the wine rack makes each bottle look like an amusing wooden Stegosaurus you can always count on to get you drunk.

Make your young adventurer’s off-road dreams come true with the Jeep Wrangler bed template. The template provides step-by-step instructions so you – or someone who’s actually handy – can craft the ultimate action bed for your adventurous offspring.

Relive the excitement and glory of old school gaming every time you utilize the Super Mario Bros mouse pad. Your mouse will glide with ease over the smooth and spacious pad styled with a classic Super Mario Bros design that is perfect for old school gamers.

Share a sacred bond with your BFF by partaking in the lifelong ritual of wearing the milk and cookies necklaces. No matter where life may take you two, as long as you both have your necklaces, you’ll be as inseparable as this classic combination.

Wear your favorite games with the Super NES cartridge ring. These nostalgic handmade gems can be completely customized to resemble your favorite Super Nintendo title and look great with any outfit – making them the ultimate retro gamer fashion accessory.

Enjoy a soft and colorful cotton candy roll without the sticky mess or unwanted calories with the cotton candy necklace. This carnival styled handmade gem features a small and colorful roll of freshly spun cotton candy that’s great for complementing any look.

Bring the Shire into your humble abode with the Lord Of The Rings Hobbit terrarium. This lovely handmade item is small enough to fit just about anywhere and gives LOTR fans a chance to gaze at the picturesque environment of our favorite Hobbits.

The chalkboard flask gives you the perfect excuse to take your hooch anywhere you go. When people question why you have a flask at the supermarket, just flash them the flask and they’ll see your shopping list jotted down – and an impromptu intervention is averted.

Becoming Dovahkiin is as easy as slipping on the crochet viking helmet. This custom made piece of apparel disguises your mere mortal self with a mighty dragonborn helmet that will also keep you warm during the merciless winter nights.

Part masterpiece, part collectible, and all around awesome – the Judge Dredd stained glass lamp is the must have accessory for any fan of the Judge. This beautifully crafted lamp illuminates the designated area while accenting the room’s decorum.

Create an eye catching look by accenting your outfit with the octopus tentacle earrings. These zany and colorful earrings are designed to look like realistic – albeit interestingly colored – octopus tentacles guaranteed to get you noticed whenever you wear them.

Stay warm by dressing up as one of Gotham’s most deranged citizens with the Harley Quinn hoodie. The hoodie is made of soft cotton accented by thick white yarn and is designed after Harley Quinn’s signature harlequin jester outfit.

One flick of the superhero <del>penis</del> light switch plate and PLOW! – your entire bedroom lights up. With these comic book styled light switch plates you’ll be able to choose your favorite superhero <del>to molest</del> to accompany you through the light and dark times.

Get up off the couch and explore new places with the Adventure Time Jake neck pillow. Jake’s taking a break from hanging with Finn and has now become your ultimate travel companion, lending his magical form shifting abilities for your comfort.

Accent your outfit like the great warriors of the East with the katana sword earrings. Forged from silver, these handmade earrings were inspired by Michonne’s badass zombie slaying katana and can be customized in size and hue to match any style.

Get your young padawan into Star Wars from a young age by building one of these geektastic Star Wars AT-AT rocker using this template. The template provides you with a step by step guide that shows you everything you need to know to make your own.

Boldly go where no geeky piece of jewelry has gone before with this stylish Starship Enterprise necklace. It’s designed in the likeness of the iconic ship from Star Trek and comes in either a rodium gold or sterling silver version decorated with diamonds.

A long time ago in a groovy galaxy far, far away – the Imperials completed construction of their far out Death Star disco ball. This unique Star Wars collectible combines groovy with geeky so you can dance the night away under the psychedelic lighting of the Death Star.

Pleasure your prostate in the most politically active way possible with the 3D printed Putin butt plug. Using the Putin butt plug you and your fellow comrades will be able to make a bold rebellious statement against Putin’s conservative views.

Get ready to roll out from the darkness of the night – into the light upon flipping the Optimus Prime stained glass lamp on. This beautifully crafted Transformers lamp captures the mighty leader of the Autobots, Optimus Prime in all his glory.

Take your love of tools and hardware into the intellectual realm by playing a game with the classic tool chess set. This handmade set contains 32 well crafted pieces made out of everyday hardware, and are power coated to give them a truly elegant finish.

Accent your heroic look with a little bit of gamer flair straight out of Hyrule with the Hylian shield earrings. These custom made earrings bear the iconic shield emblem of the Triforce along with the archaic red bird drawn below it to complete the iconic look.

Organize your personal manifestos and other literary masterpieces in true Gotham fashion with the Batman Arkham Asylum bookshelf. Each handmade bookshelf boasts a sturdy aluminum frame that forms a giant bat signal when brought together.

The Dark side has never looked as fashionable as it does with the Darth Vader ring. Not even the Dark Lord’s flowing black robes can match the beauty and craftsmanship of this hand made sterling silver ring. It’s a perfect fit for any Star Wars fan.

Unleash your smartphone’s inner beast when you set it atop the battle robot cellphone holder. This custom-made cellphone holder keeps your SkyNet ready smartphone in the upright position so it’s safe from falling over while it violently asserts its dominance.

Commit to your loved one for better or worse, in sickness and health, through space and time with the Doctor Who spinning TARDIS ring – till the end of regeneration cycles do you part. It comes in various finishes and is available in men’s and women’s sizes.

Soar as high as Apollo’s chariot wheel with the steampunk Icarus wings on your back. These steampunk styled wings are custom made from reclaimed salvaged Arbutus and are fully articulated so they can be extended at a moments notice with the pull of a handle.

Let your inner astronomer shine through in the kitchen when you prepare your meals with the solar system cutting board. This bamboo cutting board comes engraved with all of our solar system planets and provides ample space for prepping ingredients.

Harness the power of the dark side to properly clean the dirty side of your body when you scrub with the Death Star soap bar. This intricately decorated designer soap smells like a springtime meadow and obliterates germs like the planet of Alderaan.

Set phasers to engagement and boldly go where no ring has gone before with this Star Trek inspired Starship Enterprise ring. Available in various sizes and finishes, the Starship Enterprise ring is the ultimate marital ring for the Captain of your heart.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Light Bulb Sticker
content: Need a bright idea? Try hanging the glow in the dark light bulb sticker in the bedroom of your scaredy-cat offspring. The sticker is designed like an over-sized light bulb that emits a soothing greenish glow and is available in various sizes to best suit your needs.

Regardless of whether you’ve pledged your undying allegiance to the Horde or the Alliance, these handmade World of Warcraft inspired clay hearthstone earrings make an excellent wearable fashion accessory while you and your guildmates go raiding.

Charge into <del>battle</del> bedtime with a true leader by your side when you place the Halo Master Chief stained glass lamp on your nightstand. Handcrafted using the Tiffany Glass Technique, this unique stained glass lamp is a must have home lighting accessory for gamers.

Cement your bromance in true superhero fashion with the Batman and Robin BFF necklace. You and the other half of your crime fighting dynamic duo both keep a small pendant piece that when combined form an iconic bat symbol.

The Dude must abide when an opportunity to buy such a room-tying-together rug presents itself. This cult classic rug was crafted using nineteen colors of acrylic, and will be the greatest piece of home decor you’ll ever own – but well, that’s just like, uh, our opinion, man.

Increase your hipster level ten-fold when you plug in the steampunk keyboard to your computer. This beautifully made custom keyboard employs a vintage style that features a quality wooden base complemented by a genuine leather surface.

Beware when you shower for Nosferatu is never far way. The Nosferatu shower curtain is the handmade item made for cinema buffs and horror movie freaks – the curtain keeps your bathroom nice and dry while an ominous Nosferatu shaped shadow lurks about.

Sprinkle on a few pinches of darkness and punk rock to your outfit with the Misfits skull belt buckle. The buckle is handcrafted in the darkest pits of hell in the shape of the Misfits skull logo for all members of the Fiend club to wear proudly.

Turn your body into the new vessel for the mighty Krang with the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Krang belt buckle. This over-sized handmade buckle is so amazingly detailed you’ll expect Krang to come alive and start ordering you around at any second.

Get toasted apocalypse style with the zombie hand pipe. This hand blown glass pipe features a high quality and unique zombie hand design – complete with decrepit fingers and multicolored rotting flesh that are sure to have make your lungs drool once you lay your eyes on it.

Fancy up your formal wear with the wooden lapel flower. This distinguished lapel flower is made from high quality rosewood and is complemented by a lovely heather grey centerpiece that will truly accentuate any classic look.

Offset your bathroom’s girly decor with the bold look of the industrial pipe toilet paper holder. The toilet paper features a decorative red spigot you can rotate to entertain yourself while you unload some industrial size chocolate bombs in your toilet.

As far as mash-ups go, you’d be hard pressed to find an item more cleverly geeky than the pokeball Death Star shirt. The shirt’s epic design depicts an enormous pokeball shaped Death Star floating in the merciless darkness of outer space.

Achieve <del>immortality</del> eternal cleanliness when you summon the mighty Shenron with the Dragon Ball Z soap. Each handmade soap will have you feeling springtime fresh in no time at all – collect all 7 and the eternal dragon will appear to grant you a wish!

Frighten your beloved by showing them love and affection with the “Miss You” card. This mildly-murderous yet tender and thoughtful card helps your violent little heart express just how much you think about your sweetie on a daily basis – even while at the shooting range.

Expand your mind the same way Jake expands and stretches every part of his body with the Adventure Time Jake glass pipe. This custom made pipe is a true work of art – it stands at 5 inches and resembles the fearless warrior right down to his big googly eyes.

Let your romantic personality shine through – your face piercings – with the heart nose stud. This lovely stud is handcrafted from sterling silver in the shape of a small heart, whose simple and classic design combine perfectly with any look.

Decorate your young prince’s bedroom like something out of the Seven Kingdoms with the medieval castle Murphy bed. The Murphy bed comes intricately decorated to resemble a grand medieval castle, which can fold up when not in use by its royal subject.

Choose to get clean like a true champion when you shower with the Pokeball soap. This custom made soap is absolutely delightful – once you’re left feeling clean and fresh, the Pokeball soap rewards you for staying clean with an actual Pokemon inside of the ball!

Watch as Walt battles his demons by facing off against his alter ego – Heisenberg – with the Breaking Bad chess set. This custom built chess set pits Walt, Skylar, and Walt Jr. against Heisenberg and his sinister henchmen all hell bent on destroying each other.

The NES controller ring is just what you need to infuse a bit of geeky style into your ordinary look. This silver ring comes adorned with a miniature replica of the classic NES controller – expertly crafted right down to the smallest detail for maximum authenticity.

The cat tote bag is the purrrfect accessory for the crazy cat lady who wants to stay fashionable. This ultra practical tote bag features two cell phone pockets, 3D printed ears and an adorable two sided cat face design that keeps you company anywhere you go.

Hello Kitty is back and she’s ready to party mile high. The Hello Kitty glass pipe is handmade in the likeness of your favorite Japanese character, and comes with a special glow in the dark feature that transforms the pipe into a functional glow stick while in use.

titleEN: Canned Air From Around The World
content: Stop wasting money on expensive travel expenses – now you can experience the world simply by opening one of these cans of air from around the world. With everything from New York to Paris, these cans are must haves for the country hopper on a budget.

Fight against your scatterbrain tendencies with the essentials reminder doormat. This helpful doormat displays a list of the three essential items you shouldn’t leave home without so that if you happen to  forget them, the doormat will remind you about it before you walk out.

Can you name the truck with four wheel drive – smells like a steak and seats thirty-five. Canyonero! Canyonero! 12 yards long, 2 lanes wide, 65 tons of American Pride! Top of the line in utility sports, unexplained fires are a matter for the courts! Canyonero! Canyoneroooooooo!

Add a little extra suspense to your thriller novel by saving your reading place with the dead guy bookmark. This creative bookmark is handmade with extreme attention to detail to resemble a corpse from the morgue, and it even includes a tiny toe tag for added authenticity.

The modern cuckoo clock incorporates an old school element into your home’s decorum without sacrificing the room’s contemporary look. The elegant wooden exterior is styled in a minimalist fashion and can be programmed for specific times with adjustable volumes.

Strap into your four wheeled land ship like a true Star Wars fan with the Chewbacca seat belt cover. This fur covered cover is designed to make you look like Chewy. It’s not only stylish, but it’s easy to place over the seat belt and increases the comfort level when buckling up.

Cleanse yourself with arguably one of the greatest games of all time with the Legend Of Zelda: Ocarina Of Time gold plated cartridge soap bar. With a lovely “enchanted woods” scent, this incredibly detailed soap bar is a must have for Zelda fans.

Transform your puny human legs into the high tech limbs you’ve always dreamed of with the bionic leggings. The detailed design covers the entire leggings to make your legs appear like indestructible limbs designed in a secret laboratory at an undisclosed location.

Stay classy while at school or work with help from the engraved Anchor Man quote pencils. Each pencil comes engraved with one of Ron’s classic catch phrases like “Son of a bee sting” or “I’m kind of a big deal” to make the day just a tad bit more glorious.

Upgrade your appearance and attract all the geeks with the comic book sound effects headband. With embroidered action words like BAM, KABOOM, and WHAM, these custom made head bands make the ultimate geeky accessory for any comic fangirl.

Serve up some distinguished gentlemanly treats by preparing a batch with the mustache cookie cutter. This novelty cookie cutter is made from durable food safe plastic, comes in five distinct styles and works for making all sorts of mustache-shaped treats.

Add to your burgeoning collection of Whovian gear with the Doctor Who TARDIS Kindle cover. This novel cover offers your Kindle maximum protection from falls and scratches while pleasing the ocular senses with a detailed rendering of the Doctor’s TARDIS.

With the pug purse, dog lovers will be able to carry their quirky companion with them wherever they go. These custom purses offer ample room for possessions, and can be decorated with a custom high quality image of your furry friend emblazoned on the purse.

Show friends and loved ones just how much they mean to you by immortalizing their likeness with the laser cut wood pictures. These wooden portraits are the elegant and unique way to preserve a fond memory in a warm and rustic manner.

Use the Zelda NES cartridge clock to keep track of how many hours you’ve wasted away like a true gamer. This retro clock is a must have for any old school Legend Of Zelda fan, as this nostalgic clock is built using an old school NES cartridge as body.

Let it all hang out and give any curious male onlookers the weirdest boner right now with the visible uterus underwear. This mostly anatomically correct underwear displays the uterus in all its glory, allowing the exhibitionist in you to go wild while not actually getting naked.

Restore your HP after an intense gaming session with some 8-bit Zelda themed snacks created with this geeky cookie cutter. Simply mix the cookie dough with an excessive amount of sugar, apply the cookie cutter, set it in the oven, and you’ll have sugary treats in no time.

As the Star Wars Death Star grinder demonstrates, the capabilities of this space station go far beyond turning planets to dust. This hand crafted grinder contains a quality metal core designed to grind almost any herb with ease.

Let your children’s drawings come to life with these custom made stuffed animals. Ditch the mass produced garbage at the toy store and reward their creativity by having their drawings turned into hand made stuffed animals that will be their new favorite toy.

Whether your aim is to look fabulous or break into a home, the lock pick earrings are the fashion accessories you need. These elegant stainless steel earrings include everything you need to get in and out without being noticed. No one will suspect a thing.

With the Harry Potter plush pillow you’ll be able to cuddle up with your favorite Hogwart’s alum whenever you’re in need of some company. This custom made plush features Harry’s trademark round spectacles, lighting shaped scarf, and Gryffindor scarf.

Entertain bystanders with some enjoyable background music with the playable harmonica USB drive. This device offers 8 GB of storage capacity in addition to a highly portable instrument you can use to create beautiful melodies – provided you have talent.

Deck the halls with boughs of blood and gore when you decorate with the zombie Santa ornament. As this gruesomely designed ornament demonstrates, not even the world’s jolliest man will be safe from the impending zombie apocalypse.

Diamonds are rare, but not compared to meteorite or dinosaur bone. When you’re really looking to impress your significant other, nothing will demonstrate your love and commitment quite like the meteorite and dinosaur bone ring.

Wish your fellow geeky friends and family an out of this world holiday season with the Star Wars holiday cards. Each card contains one of your favorite characters such as Lando or Yoda dressed in full Christmas garments, wishing you a Merry Christmas in their own special way.

Decorate the Christmas tree with these 8-bit pixelated ornaments. Each one of these hand made ornament sets includes four 8-bit pixel art Christmas baubles. They measure between 3-4 inches, and include ornament hooks so you can hang them from your Christmas tree.

Pokemon panties. PO-KE-MON PANTIES. Let that sink in. These cute and comfy panties are designed like some of the most popular Pokemon characters – allowing you to transform your rear end into that of your favorite Pokemon.

The Super Mario World belt is geek chic at it’s best. This custom made belt sports an eye-catching flying Mario buckle, complemented by a tanned leather belt designed to look like an actual level from the classic Nintendo game. It’s the ultimate gift for the fashionable geek.

Enjoy the company of the nation’s most beloved newscaster during playtime with the Ron Burgundy LEGO. This dashing LEGO Burgundy sports his iconic mustache and comes dressed in a suit so fine it makes Sinatra look like a hobo – now to find some LEGO scotch.

Get ready to cast lightning bolts and fireballs at mighty foes while suited up in this epic battle mage armor. Hand crafted from premium 10oz leather, the strap and buckle closing outfit can be custom built to any color and size measurements requested.

Ward off ghouls, boogie men, and even Bowser himself with the Super Mario night light. This cleverly designed night light is stylish, durable, and made in the likeness of our favorite Italian plumber – making it a great accent light for any young gamer’s bedroom.

Stay warm and healthy like a true fan with the Chicago Bulls flu game socks. They’re an ode to the great Michael Jordan and capture the iconic image of Jordan hugging Scottie Pippen after the historic game against the Utah Jazz during the ’97 playoffs.

Solve the mystery of the promised cake with this solvable Portal Companion Cube themed Rubik’s Cube. Available in either the original Portal 1 Companion Cube or Portal 2 Companion Cube style, this geeky Rubik’s Cube is a must have for gamers.

Dress up like your friendly neighborhood web-slinger while you keep warm with the Spider Man beanie. This custom knit beanie doubles as a fashionable garment and mask you can actully see through – just pull the beanie down over your eyes to become Spider Man.

The sleeping mushroom fairy princess is the perfect accent for any little girls room. This tiny mushroom fairy is hand made and intricately decorated right down to the smallest detail. Your little princess will fall in love with it almost immediately.

If your furry friend isn’t so quite so furry, the dog winter suit will help maintain them warmer than a husky. The velour fleece winter suit is available in various colors and styles and is custom made to the measurements of your pooch to ensure a perfect fit.

Keep your feline friend entertained for hours on end with the Super Mario cat complex. Great for all gamers and cat lovers, this novelty item comes complete with a question box and green portals lined with sisal to help them climb in and out of the box.

Master artist Dave Pollot has a unique skill set – he finds abandoned art from thrift shops and re-paints them to look more captivating. Each work of art is a limited piece, featuring geeky additions such as Futurama and Star Wars characters.

Unleash the dragonborn warrior within with this life size Skyrim Dovahkiin iron helmet. Based on the iconic iron helmet commonly found in the video game, this highly detailed replica helmet is an absolute must have for The Elder Scrolls: Skyrim fans.

Add a touch of French-inspired fashion to any outfit with the guillotine necklace. This finely crafted necklace features a completely 3D guillotine pendant made from white bronze and accented with an oxidized sterling silver overlay to bring out the intricacies of the wood.

The Doctor Who Dalek glass pipe will take you on a mind expanding journey no TARDIS ride can match. This custom made gem delivers a concentrated dose of THC to your body with the same efficiency they shoot their death ray with – EXTERMINATE.

Solidify your relationship with your BFF with the Breaking Bad friendship necklace. These chemically pure and stable necklace pendants are perfect for those unlikely friendships we all come upon in our lives, or just for drug dealers. Friendship, bitch!

Flaunt it if you’ve got it with the ass cleavage underwear. Deemed too sexy for traditional stores such as Victoria’s Secret, this revealing pair of underwear will highlight your best asset, and also makes squeezing out a chocolate hot dog a much simpler and faster process.

Start your day off like a true gamer by showering with the NES controller soap bar. This delightfully scented bar of soap is styled exactly like the classic NES controllers we all grew up on – right down to the tiniest detail. A must have for any gamer’s bathroom.

titleEN: Han Solo Frozen In Carbonite Ring
content: Carry one of the greatest scenes in cinematic history wherever you go with the Han Solo frozen in carbonite ring. This limited edition ring depicts the heroic Captain Han Solo after he was captured and trapped in carbonite. A great piece of flair for any Star Wars fan.

Experience what it’s like to get cuffed without having to actually get arrested by accessorizing your outfit with the handcuff ring. The ring is made from steel titanium and is designed like an exact replica of  a real handcuff. It even includes a functioning lock and key.

It’s dangerous to go alone – take this Triforce bra! Inspired by the iconic Legend of Zelda franchise, this hand painted bra features the bold styling of the Triforce design on an eye catching royal blue backdrop that every princess will be dying to wear.

The Nintendo controller iPhone charger has old and new technology teaming up to aid you on your daily activities. The charger is made from an authentic NES controller and provides an amusing way for all gamers to charge their iPhones.

Style yourself with jewelry inspired by one of the most infamous intergalatic bounty hunters from a galaxy far, far away. The ring is crafted in the likeness of the iconic helmet worn by Boba Fett, and is available in an affordable sterling silver or eye catching platinum.

Dr. Heiter is at it again, creating yet another masterpiece of digestive efficiency with the my little pony centipede. This horrifically detailed doll depicts three little ponies surgically bound together from ass to mouth so the excrement of one is the food of another.

Look sexy like a fox with this foxy underwear. These custom made cotton undies are as adorable and unique as they are comfy. Each pair features a cute little maroon and white fox complete with hand sewn facial features and two little fox ears to complete the look.

The countless hours you spent wrangling up stray Pokemon on your Game Boy would mean nothing without the Pokemon trainer badges. These custom made badges are the ideal way to validate your long and arduous journey to becoming a true Pokemon master.

The Breaking Bad Heisenberg cufflinks are just like Walt – understated yet imposing. These handmade cufflinks are made in his likeness and display his signature pork-pie hat and sunglasses. A great piece of flair for all Breaking Bad fans.

Give your offspring an out of this world gift with the Transformers Optimus Prime plushie. This soft and cuddly Transformer is made from felt in the likeness of the great and powerful leader of the Autobots – Optimus Prime. It makes a great gift for fans of the classic cartoon.

Welcome, all guests are, when you place the Yoda welcome doormat by the front door. This clever doormat displays Yoda’s portrait over a short welcome message all guests – especially Star Wars fans – will enjoy. It’s the ideal house warming gift for any Sci-Fi fan.

Take your favorite band of talking toys along wherever you go with the Toy Story shoes. These classic slip-on Vans feature a custom graphic of Woody, Buzz, Rex and the rest of the gang drawn in amazing detail. You definitely have a friend in these shoes.

The Donkey Kong blanket is a handcrafted rendition of the original video game released in 1981. Every ladder, barrel, and even Mr. Kong himself are knitted from acrylic thread so you can stay warm during the winter months while reminiscing about this classic game.

Protect yourself from possible Predators with the Xenomorph brass knuckles ring. This fierce piece of jewelry doubles as a stylish fashion accessory and self defense weapon. The Xenomorph ring stretches out and instantly transforms into deadly brass knuckles.

Hey girl, if you want to see Ryan Gosling’s perfect face everyday then you need to buy yourself a pair of these stud earrings. With two times the Gosling, you’ll be getting a double stuff of the most handsome man on the planet that will have you smiling from ear to ear.

Look no further than the Super Mario piranha sculptures to add the perfect touch to any gamer’s bedroom. These hand sculpted works of art portray the deadly piranha plants from the classic Mario Bros. game in stunning detail – a great gift for any old school gamer.

Count on the bleeding hand candle to lend a helpful yet eerily disturbing hand next time the power goes out. This unique candle comes shaped like a dismembered hand and creates the illusion it’s bleeding out once the red wax on the interior of the candle begins to melt.

Restore yourself to full health points and full hygiene points simultaneously with the Zelda heart shaped soap bar. Featuring a suspended cherry center and a translucent light blue outer shell, the Zelda themed heart soap bar is the perfect gift idea for smelly gamers.

Look like a reading aficionado while you get drunk off your ass with the hollow book and flask. This dynamic duo makes you appreciate classic literature like never before. The book conceals a hollowed out interior shaped to perfectly cradle a nice full flask of hard liquor.

Power up your afternoon meals by encasing them inside a recycled NES lunchbox. This one of a kind lunchbox is made from a re-purposed original Nintendo console and features a high quality handle to accent the look. Your young gamer will be the envy of every kid at school.

Just in time for All Hallows Eve comes Halloweenstown’s hottest import – the Nightmare Before Christmas Sally ragdoll dress. With custom stitching and vibrant colors, this hand made dress is designed to look like the dress Sally wore in the film.

Cuddle up to the sea’s most friendly and lovable monster with the giant Cthulu plushie and experience the warm embrace as its nine ancient tentacles hug you tightly while the dark lord whispers sweet nothings of a language long forgotten to lull you to sleep.

This is no Jedi mind trick, these truly are the double droids you’re looking for. The hand painted R2-D2 bra converts your boring biological breasts into mechanical wonders of engineering that will have every intergalactic space criminal drooling over them.

Stay warm while you study for the big biology test with the body anatomy sweatshirt. This stylish pink sweatshirt features a stitched on textbook-like graphic mapping out the human body’s internal organs – it’s educational fashion at its best.

The Nightmare Before Christmas bottle makes the ideal accessory for any geeky outfit. This handmade pendant creates a surreal landscape inspired by the singular visual style of director Tim Burton. It’s a pendant with artwork as unique as the director himself.

No sexy nurse, fairy, or butterfly costume would be complete without the maggot infested throat necklace. This graphic and revolting costume prop will have all others staring in astonishment and disgust as plump maggots spew out of your festering open wound.

Bring a little Jedi zen into your life with the Master Yoda terrarium. This terrarium will sit perfectly on your porch or in your kitchen to give you a little bit of the spiritual Yoda guidance you’ve been seeking all your life. An eco-friendly moss terrarium it is!

Show off that award winning smile wherever you go by accessorizing with the denture bracelet. This unique and hand made bracelet showcases two rows of pearly whites that have been shined to a nice glossy finish. They’re perfect for complementing any outfit.

Add some life to any dull story by saving your place with the cabaret legs bookmark. Sporting a pair of sexy black heels, these sultry stems will have you turning off the tv and reaching for the <del> woman trapped inside</del> thrilling story you’re currently reading.

The bloody cleaver ring is just the accessory you’ll need to put the finishing touches on any Halloween costume this Fall. While worn, the bloody cleaver ring creates the illusion your fingers are being brutally chopped off by a razor sharp cleaver.

Don’t get lost in the treacherous land of <del>vagina</del> Hyrule – simply look at your underwear for guidance with these Zelda panties. These geeky panties feature an elastic waistband for your comfort, and can be custom ordered with specific areas from the Link’s Awakening map.

Mirror mirror on the wall, who’s the fastest ship of them all? Why, the Millennium Falcon of course! Each one of these geeky Millennium Falcon mirrors are hand-made and hand-painted, and make an excellent gift for the Star Wars fan who appreciates fine craftsmanship.

The Empire Strikes Book with this Imperial AT-AT bookcase. This hand-made piece is a must have collectible for Star Wars fans – and is perfect for displaying your books and memorabilia in geeky fashion.

Kevin Flynn has become one with the system now that his portrait has been etched on this TRON themed circuit board. This artistic circuit board displays the message “Flynn lives” right under his portrait – a must have for any TRON fan and/or sci-fi enthusiast.

Pay tribute to America’s most bad-ass President with the historically accurate Roosevelt vs. Bigfoot painting. This glorious painting depicts Teddy Roosevelt gunning down the mighty Big Foot as he cleared the way for the construction of the Panama canal.

Turn those pesky invading sea tentacles into helpful storage devices with the tentacle wall hanger. Perfect for organizing your stuff, the tentacle wall hanger’s multiple curved arms easily handle keys, necklaces, rings, or just about anything you can hang.

Play a game of Simon anytime and anywhere with this functional Simon belt buckle. This classic game of memory testing will now not only provide you with hours of portable entertainment, but it will also add a splash of nostalgia to your wardrobe.

Add to your collection of bottled Poe souls without ever having to battle Poe himself with these mini glow in the dark necklaces. Available in a variety of colors, each bottled Poe soul is hand painted and fixed in place with a transparent gel.

Protect the weakest point of entry – the glass window – with one of the most decorated heroes of our generation with the Halo Master Chief. This handmade masterpiece features the legendary Master Chief standing guard, crafted out of roughly 200 pieces of glass.

Never before has a plump patty, lettuce, and pickles looked more appealing than on the cheeseburger pillow. Made from recycled fabrics, this loaded pillow comes with all the fixings and condiments you’ll need to relax as you lay down on the soft buns.

Sometimes you just don’t feel like doing anything at work or school. For those days that seems to drag on endlessly, try using a “fuck this shit’ pencil. Each pencil displays a short and friendly message to communicate to the rest of the world just how much you want to be there.

Flair up your home like any respected environmental friendly Pokemon master would with a few of the wood burned Pokeballs. Although they’re not designed to capture real life Pokemon, they’re great for adding a touch of rustic elegance to the room.

Give new life to your significant other when you bestow upon them the most revitalizing gift in all of Hyrule, the Zelda heart shaped pendant. This hand crafted pendant displays a lovely crimson heart encased in a bright field of blue – a must have for those looking to boost their HP.

Before the Dark Knight donned his high tech suit, a great ancestor of his battled dragons and wizards in the medieval Batman armor. The custom designed bat helmet is complimented by a full suit of armor that includes a metallic Batman logo emblazoned over the front.

Keep your humble abode looking classy with the Alien facehugger wall clock hanging on the wall. This eye catching clock displays a copper toned facehugger latching onto a large black plate, while each conveniently placed arm helps point out the time.

There’s no better symbol of friendship in the entire galaxy than the C-3PO R2D2 heart necklace. You and your BFF will each get to take one half of the dynamic robot duo that when joined together, form a cool and geeky heart shape.

There’s no better knick-knack for your burgeoning collection of fourth dimensional objects than the world’s smallest Klein bottle. This self contained bottle is approximately 1 1/4″ tall and hand blown by an expert artisan out of a durable borosilicate glass.

Easily switch to the Dark Side when you install one of these Star Wars Alliances themed light switches in your home. With the flick of the switch you can join an elite group of galaxy peacekeepers, or succumb to the temptations of the Dark Side as night falls.

Nothing will keep those unwanted visitors away from your home quite like the go away bite mark doormat. If the straight forward message isn’t enough to deter guests from your humble abode, the fierce bite mark will get the message across loud and clear.

Dress up as Arkham Asylum’s most dedicated and professional psychiatrist with the Harley Quinn costume. This hand crafted costume features intricate detailing and a vibrant contrast of colors guaranteed to make you the center of attention anywhere you wear it.

Add a little macabre decor to your home with the  skull sculpture. This custom-made sculpture displays a unique pattern, which gives a 360 degree view of the skull inside and out so you get to appreciate its intricate detailing. It also makes a great Halloween time decoration.

Count your blessings and say your prayers with these Star Wars prayer candles. Whether you wish to pray to the Dark Side or whisper sweet nothings to the Queen of the Rebel scum, there is truly a prayer candle for every type of blasphemous Star Wars geek out there.

Show your love of Nutella while staying fashionable at all times with the Nutella ring. This cute accessory contains a miniature and realistically portrayed Nutella bottle resting on an elegant steel band ideal for sweetening up any outfit.

Bring sexy back to the Mushroom Kingdom with this head turning Super Mario latex outfit. This skintight latex outfit consists of high waisted capri leggings and a crop top designed to mimic our favorite Yoshi-riding, mushroom-eating, princess-saving Italian plumber.

Keep track of every single inch you burn off while on your diet with the measuring tape belt. This helpful belt displays measurements in both inches and centimeters so you can easily keep track of your progress no matter what system of measurement you abide by.
