Transform your trusty steed into a magical creature with the unicorn horn horse attachment. This imaginative attachment goes on the top brow of the horse and fits comfortably as you ride your – silver or golden horned – unicorn.

It’s dangerous to go alone – take this blankie! Featuring the nostalgic quote from the wise old bearded man from the original NES Legend of Zelda video game – this clever acrylic throw blanket is perfect for the young princess saver in your family.

Unlock the true power of the Triforce while you get absolutely hammered with the Legend Of Zelda bottle opener. Built out of premium ten gauge steel, the sturdy Zelda themed bottle opener’s sword also functions as a means of puncturing and shotgunning beers.

Your baby may be too young to save princesses and conquer water temples – but he’s never too young to  be dressed in legendary style. With the Zelda inspired Link onesie you can dress your little hero and make him a hit at the playgrounds.

Jewelry with fluffy hearts and cute pendants won’t save your ass when all hell breaks loose, but the zombie apocalypse tools bracelet might. It includes all the reminder charms you’ll need for survival from canned food for nourishment. a compass, and ax to help your survive.

Add a touch of magic to your plain muggle bathroom with the Ministry of Magic toilet decal. Now Harry Potter fans will be able to send their <del>waste</del> unwanted guests to the magical realm of wizards and witches instead of those rat infested city sewers.

In Zelda: Ocarina of Time, one of the best Nintendo games ever, the Zelda Kokiri Forest Emerald is the stone that guides Link from the Deku tree. Guide yourself with this Kokiri Forest Emerald necklace, designed to make you look, feel, and think just like Link.

Complete your killer dinosaur costume by adding the perfect finishing touch with the triceratops copper mask. Crafted by hand, this intricately designed mask works as both a fashion accessory or as an abstract piece of dino art for the home.

Increase your offspring’s cuteness factor tenfold when you dress them up with the Cabbage Patch Kids wig. Available as a sewing pattern or as a finished hat, these cute wigs come in a variety of colors so your kids can look like a cuddly doll no matter what the occasion.

As long as you have the children’s books necklace your favorite literary works will always remain close to your heart. Each pendant is designed to resemble a classic book and houses two pictures on the inside – the ideal gift for any avid reader.

What better way to combine your love of paleontology and botany than with the dinosaur planters. These vibrant planters are available in several species of dinosaurs so you can choose your favorite one or give the perfect gift to the dino lover with a green thumb.

Make your feet look like the most delicious of all foods with sandwich sandals, the flip flops that look like loaded up sammies. Although these shoes don’t feel as squishy as really wearing sandwiches on your feet, you’ll find them far more stylish.

Stay warm like a true hero with the Legend of Zelda Link hoodie. This geeky article of clothing comes equipped with its own Hylian Shield and Master Sword sewn into the hoodie just in case you plan on attacking leaves of grass and pots full of rupees.

Add a fun factor to bath time by showering with the tetris soap. These handmade soaps come available in different fragrances and features seven distinct tetris pieces that actually fit together so you can play a quick game while you shower and ponder life’s great mysteries.

Real friends are like pizza, they come in all toppings and are always welcome. The pizza slice necklace allows you and your closest eight home slices to partake in the sacred bond of friendship by each holding on to their very own golden slice of pie – also available in veggie.

The pentagram bikini will give you some hot satanic tan lines guaranteed to drive all the goth boys crazy. This two piece custom string bikini  features a sinister jet black pentagram displayed over the front that’ll turn heads at any beach, pool, or lake of fire.

Build the ultimate line of defense against waves of zombies by sewing some of these Plants Vs. Zombies plushies. Each pattern pack includes instructions to construct sunflowers, wall-nuts, and pea shooter plants so you can conquer those darn whippersnapper zombies.

It’s doesn’t get much geekier and naughtier than the latex Batman underwear. These sexy and nerdy panties display Batman’s logo across the rear-end against a white backdrop of white to make it stand out as it accentuates the body’s natural curves.

Don’t worry if your career plans don’t work out because with the Goonies Doubloon replica in your hands, One Eyed Willie’s treasure is yours for the taking. This replica contains all the same markings necessary to lead you and a rag tag group of friends to great riches.

No matter what Pokemon pipe you choose, the adventures you’ll embark on with your new companion are guaranteed to give you a magical experience. Once they learn moves like the THC tackle and Mary Jane sweep your pipe will become unstoppable.

Save the princess from danger and then save yourself from disgusting body odor with these Legend of Zelda themed rupee soap bars. Each set comes with four differently colored rupee soap bars, so you can bathe yourself in various Hyrule denominations.

This baby cowboy hat crochet pattern creates a beautiful cowboy hat for your little cowpoke or cowgirl. All those baby beanies shaped like owls are kinda cute, but this hat lends your kid an air of mystery and icy cold determination. Just get to stitchin’!

No matter how friendless or unpopular you are, wearing the Daft Punk costume for a night on the town will get you access into any club or party, no questions asked. Once you don Thomas Bangalter’s famous costume, velvet ropes will part and panties will drop.

Take advantage of your second amendment right, even while you shower by bringing the gun soap into the tub or shower. The soap bars combine the essence of America with the most intoxicating aromas around – guaranteed to leave any gun enthusiast spring time clean.

titleEN: School Of Hard Knocks Class Ring
content: Graduating from a prestigious Ivy League institution will pale in comparison to being an ex-alum of the School of Hard Knocks. Just one glance of this distinguished and noble class ring is enough to make future employers hire you on the spot.

Control the lighting in your home using spells and wizardry with this Harry Potter light switch sticker. The sticker is easy to apply and displays the “Lumos” and “Nox” spells over the switch – the ideal way to add a touch of magic to your dull muggle home.

You’ll definitely be “thinking different” when you decide to house your pet in one of the recycled iMac pet beds. The beds are made using hollowed out iMacs that have been re-purposed as snug and comfy homes great for small cats and dogs.

Comb your hair or trendy mustache in the most fashionable way possible with a few strokes with the whale shaped comb. This hand made gem is available in various colors and features a playful design that’ll catch the attention of anyone around.

titleEN: My Side Your Side Pillow Cases
content: Relationships are all about setting boundaries, and to help you set them in the bedroom, here are the ‘my side’ ‘your side’ pillow cases. Each case comes in fashionable white linen and features helpful labels that help you take over 3/4 of the bed to yourself – equality.

Add a peculiar touch to any room with the hanging jellyfish plant. With an overhead dome base and long thin vines, the airplant masquerades as a jellyfish that gracefully floats about the room like a candy wrapper caught in an updraft.

Transform your puny human face into something more respectable – like the face of the great Cthulhu – with this full face leather Cthulhu mask. It’s the perfect accessory for reigning over the planet Earth in a dark period of around over 3000 years.

Add an ultra geeky and stylish component to your PC or laptop with the GameBoy external hard drive. Each drive is made from a retired and hollowed out GameBoy that houses a reliable 500GB-1TB hard drive. For greater convenience, it’s powered soley by a USB cable.

titleEN: Center Of The Universe Cat Hat
content: Give your “center of the universe” cat a fitting crown with this solar system cat hat. This cleverly designed handmade hat has all of the planets orbiting around your cat, proving without a doubt that your charming feline is the absolute center of the universe.

The nixie tube clock will bring a unique touch to any room with its eye-catching design. The custom made clock is composed of six independent nixie tubes that display the time and date through a dazzling display of neon lights.

With Los Pollos Hermanos meth buckets at your disposal, your up and coming meth business will discretely prosper. They provide the perfect front for transporting illicit materials and come with delicious candy inside — you’ll be Kingpin of the local drug market in no time at all.

You ever have the feeling someone is watching you? Well, if you’re eating a dinosaur eye lollipop then you’d be right. Each freakishly delicious lollipop is flavored like cotton candy and comes with a unique eye design that peers into your soul with every lick.

Take jolly old England’s character building gloomy weather wherever you go with the rain cloud necklace. The necklace features a cute cloud pendant made from wool that includes three blue crystal beads to symbolize the raindrops.

Carry your rupees, bombs, arrows, and other hero-like items around with this Zelda Hylian shield backpack. It’s a must have functional piece of gear for the Zelda fan – and no <del>virgin</del> Master Sword wielding princess rescuer should be without one.

Prepare to have others look at you with pure envy when you show up with the LEGO brick bag on your shoulders. Its nostalgic design pays homage to the classic LEGO block while its boxy shape provides ample room for all your belongings.

Introducing the latest design straight off the Aperture Laboratories production line, these highly experimental and wildly unstable Portal earrings are a must have for gamers. You also get your choice of sterling silver or gold for these geeky stud earrings.

Look like one of the most iconic and exotic Disney princesses of all time with the Little Mermaid costume. This handcrafted masterpiece displays such a high level of artistry you’ll swear the seashells were taken directly from the kingdom of Atlantica.

The crayon fake gauge earrings allow you to look wild and rebellious without having to make and permanent body modifications. Upon screwing the two halves in together, they create the appearance the earlobe’s been skewered by a crayon.

No man cave would be complete without the vintage beer can lamp. The frame features a mint condition tall boy 16 oz Budweiser can sitting on a wooden base and complimented by a hand-made pull tab lamp shade that creates a one of a kind lighting pattern.

Fight off armies of deadites with the chainsaw dress. This lovely and graphic dress is emblazoned with a bloody chainsaw draped over the front that creates the illusion you’re wielding it on the stomp of your hand once your hand enters the pocket.

Lawn gnomes just became obsolete. Protect your home from solicitors and burglars with this life size Transformers Bumblebee statue. Standing over seven and half feet tall, this Transformers statue will easily become your favorite home decoration.

For science! No matter how impressive you think your art collection is, it’ll never be “Carl Sagan riding a dinosaur while wielding a lightsaber” impressive, unless you purchase the painting. It also makes a great centerpiece in any internet based circlejerk.

The Pi bottle opener proves that math is actually useful in your day to day life. Even if you’re not able to recite pi to the second decimal point, this geeky bottle opener allows you to appreciate mathematics just like if you were one of the smart kids.

The monster coffee mug is ideal for expressing how you feel every morning you wake up too early to go to school or work. This custom made mug contains a monstrous growling mouth that warns others to keep away until after you’ve had your morning cup of coffee.

Make your earlobes into octopus tentacles with rainbow tentacle faux earplugs. If you don’t want to commit to widening your earring holes and stretching your lobes, these rainbow plugs will fool even the cleverest eye — and they have enough fab to brighten your day.

Walk into the the Halloween ball as the best dressed zombie when you wear the undead tights. These gruesome tights will turn the healthiest looking pair of legs into pale, rotting stumps a decaying zombie such as yourself would be proud to show off.

No matter what the occasion, the Pikachu necklace is the piece of jewelry you’ll choose. The elegant necklace displays a custom cut nickel silver Pikachu pendant guaranteed to make your outfit pop. It’s the ideal statement for the fashion forward Pokemon geek.

Finalize your divorce by severing off your ring finger with this guillotine ring. This morbid jewelry piece makes an excellent gift for a recent divorcees, and lets potential cougars and manthers know that you are single and ready to mingle.

Get cuddly with your favorite Minecraft villain with this life-size creeper pillow. This massive 60″ pillow makes an excellent gift for Minecraft fans, and can even be requested in non-traditional creeper colors such as orange, red, blue, and pink.

Prepare your children for battle against the Imperial army with this Star Wars themed Ewok hat. These geeky yet fearsome furball hats will give your offspring the courage they need to bash a stormtrooper’s head in while looking absolutely adorable.

Your little blockhead will have nothing to say ‘good grief’ about when you dress him up in the Charlie Brown onesie. It displays the iconic black zig-zag line against an all yellow background in a comfortable and easy to to remove garment perfect for any infant.

Gotta cup ’em all! With the Pokemon themed pokebra your twins can be converted into overflowing pokeballs that every nerd will be dying to unleash! These Pokemon bras are custom made so geeks of any shape and size can have their goodies properly supported.

Winter is coming – in LEGO form!  These custom made LEGO figurines feature all your favorite still living – for now – characters from the Game Of Thrones series. These are limited edition LEGOs, and are a must have collectible for Game Of Thrones fans.

Toss out that old Victoria’s Secret lingerie and spoil that special geek in your life by surprising him/her with this sexy TRON corset. This lovely outfit will glow if exposed to bright light – such as UV light – making you look like a sexy character out of the TRON franchise.

Bathe your dark passenger in Dexter Morgan like fashion with this “Slice of Life” decal for your bathtub. It’s the perfect bathroom decor if you love the show Dexter but don’t own a boat – best of all they can be removed without sticky <del>forensic evidence</del> residue being left behind.

Bring new life to your gaming room when you install this Super Metroid stained glass. No detail was spared in creating this masterful stained glass modeled after the iconic Samus Aran in her orange Varia suit – making it an instant collectible for Metroid fans.

You won’t believe how adorable your hands will look with the sloth rings adorning your fingers. Each adjustable ring is made with a silver finish and contain a lethargic sloth so cheerful and cute he’ll brighten up your day every time you look at your hand.

Who knew the Dark Side of the Force was so kinky? With the Star Wars themed lightsaber spank toy you can fulfill all of your geeky BSDM fantasies while simultaneously destroying all of your wonderfully innocent childhood memories of the Star Wars movies.

No shrine to Star Wars would be complete without the Stormtrooper stained glass adorning a window or wall. The masterfully crafted piece depicts the <del>deadly marksman</del> Stormtrooper with blaster in hand as he get ready to fire <del>aimlessly</del> at his desired target.

Keep the last Metroid in captivity by chaining it around your neck with this beautiful Super Metroid necklace. Available in brass, sterling silver, or twenty four carat gold, these gem studded Metroid necklaces make an excellent gift idea for an intergalactic bounty hounter.

Use the bearded Rastafarian hat to unleash your inner <del>stoner</del> rasta without permanently trading in the more conservative look your office job demands of you. This knit beard and dread combo not only alters your appearance but also keeps you warm in cold weather.

We pity the fool that don’t use the Mr. T teapot for afternoon tea and crumpets because this unique teapot is the complete package. Apart from enjoying the sight of Mr. T’s epic mohawk, the teapot’s design allows you to stack the pot on top of the mug for easy storage.

Increase your food supply while upgrading your crafting skills when you spawn the Zerg Overlord plush sewing pattern. This cloaked unit detecting plushie can be crafted by virtually anyone with a sewing machine and is great for scouting the neighborhood for cheesers.

Stop, pause, move left, and move right with the Playstation button earrings. These earrings honor the magnificent Playstation, the game console that brought game graphics into the twentieth century. When you wear them, you can imagine yourself as a console.

There are too many sexy kitties and sexy witches at costume parties. Keep the spirit of dressing up in horrific – but still sexy – manner with these ripped flesh garters. You’ll look like you’ve hooked up your lingerie to your decaying flesh – hot!

You’ll never have to say goodbye to your favorite gaming console thanks to the N64 controller desk organizer. This re-purposed controller is hollowed out so every pen and pencil you have scattered on your desk can remain organized and always at hand.

Spoil your little princess and make her wishes come true with the life size My Little Pony. This enormous and cuddly pony sports a soft and colorful coat of fur complimented by a luxurious brightly colored mane and tail your little girl will go crazy over.

Upgrade your fashion sense to legendary fiction levels with this organic cotton Little Red Riding Hood cloak. This cloak is as soft and comfortable as it is tempting for wild predators, and it may incite gentleman callers to eat your relatives, so beware!

titleEN: Super Mario Match Game Wall Prints
content: Try out your luck with these Super Mario match game wall prints. Inspired from the mini-game featured in Super Mario 3, these highly portable and extremely nostalgic wall prints can be arranged to show a winning spin or an artistically disastrous fold.

Stand your ground during the upcoming Alien invasion with this replica P-5000 power loader. Perfect for picking up and moving around heavy objects – or fighting an invading race of Xenomorphs – the P-5000 replica exoskeleton is a must have collectible.

Honor the man that brought you into this world on Father’s Day with this clever Darth Vader card that reminds us all that there are many worse father figures out there. This humorous Father’s Day card is the perfect gift for a geeky and/or neglectful Dad.

When playing a slow melody opt for the snail-shaped ukulele. This handcrafted ukulele will sound quaint and lovely when strummed, and its snail-shape and detailing will add extra, super cuteness. The ukulele is made of hard maple and hand painted.

Sushi and cake don’t usually go too well together, but these sushi cake pops are a true example defying the odds. With these cake pops, you get a tasty sugary sweet in the form of a perfect rice ball topped with nori, salmon, tuna, or wasabi.

It may not be a narwhal launching a baconator into the sun, but the Reddit upvote/downvote earrings are still a great way to show off your geeky internet ties. True to Reddit, these dangly laser cut acrylic earrings feature both the blue downvote and orange upvote.

Now you can enjoy everyone’s least favorite Halloween candy all year round without actually having to eat it — just wear this cute candy corn hat. This crocheted hat follows the color scheme perfectly with yellow, orange, and white – without the disgusting flavor!

You can keep the weird little house on the hill in your office with the lovingly crafted Beetlejuice terrarium. The iconic haunted house from the most excellent Tim Burton movie stands one and a half inches tall, and it sits atop hills of living, sustainably harvested moss.

You may not be of noble birth, but that doesn’t mean you can’t sit on your own throne. With the Game Of Thrones inspired toilet decal, you can turn your boring porcelain shit receptacle into a glorious iron throne that will strike fear into the heart of your enemies.

titleEN: Han Solo Frozen Light Switch Cover
content: Complete your Star Wars themed room with this Han Solo frozen in carbonite light switch cover. Though his body may be frozen, his ‘lightsaber’ remains functional and acts as the on and off switch – which only adds to Han Solo’s undeniable sex appeal.

Venus flytraps may be cool but they have nothing on the Super Mario piranha plant. This rare beauty of the plant world is made from custom beads to recreate the classic 8-bit look and come in various poses and sizes ideal for decorating any game room.

HEY! LISTEN! Whether you need to freeze an enemy or light a torch halfway across the room, these Legend of Zelda inspired elemental arrow keychains will be sure to do the trick. Available in either light, fire, or ice arrow style, they make for the ultimate in geeky jewelry.

As the cat paper lampshade demonstrates, there’s no such thing as going overboard with cat themed decorations for the home. This kitty inspired custom lampshade features a minimalist design that seems to transform entirely once the lights come on.

If those mounted deer heads are a bit gaudy for your taste, switch over to the deer antler switchplate. The switchplates allow any hunting enthusiast to tastefully decorate their home while also providing a handy spot to hang keys and other knick-knacks.

Who needs guard dogs or fancy security systems when you have the giant metal dragon magnificently towering over your humble abode. This imposing dragon is custom made entirely from metal and stands at over 10 feet tall so all who visit can awe in amazement.

Secure your home with the crème de la crème of 90s technology with the GoldenEye 007 remote mine. You’ll be arming your home with nostalgic weapons – equipped with working LEDs – faster than you can detonate them on your enemies.

You don’t need to be a skilled ocarina player, or have any musical talent for that matter, in order to enjoy the Legend of Zelda songring. Cast in stainless steel, the ring displays the music to the most memorable tunes from the Ocarina of Time.

Complete your Boba Fett costume with this hand made Boba Fett helmet. Crafted using liquid resin and featuring extreme attention to detail, the iconic Mandalorian helmet worn by the infamous bounty hunter can now be yours!

Live out your childhood dream of being a mighty robot when you put on the Ninja Turtles Krang apron. The apron comes with a design that turns the entire torso into Krang’s colossal robotic exoskeleton – complete with the pinkish, brain-like Krang housed in the middle.

Wallets are for chumps, if you really want to tote around your fat stack of dough like a true shot-caller you need the AK-47 money clip. This bad-ass gold plated clip securely hugs your dough while its menacing AK-47 frame warns others to keep their distance.

Now with the Zelda apron you’ll be able to remain at the forefront of Hyrulian fashion even when you’re stuck at home <del>smashing pots</del> doing chores. Each apron is made entirely from cotton for the most comfortable fit possible and comes in either a Zelda or Toon Link design.

Ditch those conventional designer scarves and opt to show off your more industrial side when you begin sporting the knitted power cord. These quirky garments are entirely hand-made and are available in the classic safety orange color in addition to many others.

You don’t have to be part of House Targaryen to get your hands on some rare and valuable dragon eggs. These custom-made eggs make excellent centerpieces and are available in the color styles shown on the TV series or from the book.

Who needs Victoria Secret when you happen to have the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles bra in your collection of intimates? These unique bras are hand painted with extreme detail to mimic the face of your favorite pizza-eating, crime-fighting, sewer-surfing turtles.

Take home a piece of vampire hunting history when you acquire the steampunk bow. This bow is fashioned from sturdy plastic and metal and designed to deliver a deadly stake through the chest of any undead monster; a must have for anyone planning a trip to Transylvania.

The crocheted Tetris pillow is shown here in the shape of the useful, yet infuriating, step-shaped Tetris piece. This piece could be guided on top of Tetris protrusions of any size. Guide it to the side of your sofa and either pummel it or cuddle it, depending on your mood.

Become the picture of pure evil after donning the Borderland Psycho Bandit mask at the next convention. The mask portrays the demented psycho bandit and features amazing attention to detail in addition to LED eyes that enhance the menacing appeal.

The perfect couch for any aspiring vampire, this coffin couch features a plush violet interior and a hardwood exterior. It folds away for day time rest, and opens up at night when its owner goes on the prowl. This sofa gives any apartment an Addams family vibe.

With the peanut butter and jelly pillows you can finally enjoy a tasty snack without worrying about adding extra junk in the trunk. These scrumptious looking pillows are so comfy and plump, we’re willing to bet you’ll enjoy them even more than a real PB&J sandwich.

Just one morsel of the Star Wars chocolate is enough to send you flying with ecstasy to Tatooine’s second sun. Meticulously crafted by an expert chocolatier, these delicious treats feature all the classic shapes and characters like R2-D2 and the evil Darth Vader.

Make a splash at the next ball as you promenade into the room with the majestic swan wig. It’s woven from a blend of fine silk, alpaca, and adorned with pearls to make this Elizabethan inspired masterpiece a must-have for any <del>worst</del> best dressed list.

Eat your precious baby up just like you want to with the shark attack sleeping bag. This sleeping bag is the perfect gift for a new parent with a sense of humor — just slip the bag over baby’s legs, and it’s perfect for the stroller and just as cute as can be.

Add some excitement to the living room by sitting in front of these Couch Fighter wall decals and conjure some hadokens while you battle with your couchmate. You can take on a new identity every time you sit by the decal, and will be perfecting ultra combos in no time.

Level up your collection of geeky jewelry with one of these nostalgic Nintendo cartridge rings. Available in a variety of styles – including the legendary gold Zelda cartridge – these highly detailed rings are the perfect gift idea for the old school gamer.

The floppy disk notebook makes use of the floppy disk that got you started in your computing life. Two floppy disks encase a useful ruled notebook that can store all of your secrets. The notebook has just about as much storage as a single floppy disk, too.

Contact the unknown without drawing attention from the feds when wearing the E.T. ring. The ring’s accurate portrayal of E.T. will satisfy even the most hardcore movie fan while its antiquated copper finish make it great for all occasions, from formal events to phoning home.

Celebrate your greater piratey nature with the octopus ear cuff. The ear cuff is made of antiqued bronze, and each tentacle is exquisitely handcrafted. Requiring no piercings to be worn, this ear cuff is the perfect maritime jewelry piece.

Stop wasting precious energy using your facial muscles to express your perplexed look of disapproval – now you can simply wear these glasses and sport a disapproving face all day long! These reactionary emoticon inspired glasses are a must have for neckbeards.

Keep warm without losing the menacing appeal you’ve worked so hard to acquire with the crocheted Bane mask. It’s the one of a kind hand-knit piece of winter wear guaranteed to keep you safe and cozy whether you’re terrorizing Gotham or skiing down the slopes.

Take the law into your own hands with this replica Judge Dredd ‘Lawgiver’ gun. This incredibly detailed replica prop is designed to look just like it did in the comic book and movie, and is guaranteed to make punks show you some respect on the street.

Form truly meets function with this beautiful steampunk wireless wrist keyboard. This hand made keyboard will make you feel like a mad Steampunk genius typing away wireless commands to your giant metal Spider machine as you wreak havoc on your enemies.

Keep track of your offspring’s growth spurts with this oversized ruler growth chart. This cleverly designed piece will replace those ugly pencil marks on your walls with a gigantic and beautiful hand painted and hand distressed ruler that will add character to any kid’s room.

With these horror movie lawn gnomes you can finally hang out with your old pals Freddy, Jason, and Michael without fear of ending up in the city morgue. These meticulously decorated gnomes provide curb appeal and keep those annoying neighbors away.

Now you can increase your productivity from 0 to 60 in a matter of seconds when you use the Corvette desk to complete your work assignments. This devilishly sexy desk features a handmade design and paint job detailed enough to rival an actual Corvette.

You don’t have to be from Mordor, or even a LOTR fan to enjoy the delicious Eye of Sauron lollipops. These custom made treats feature an all-knowing, captivating eye design encased in dark sugar and covered with a clear coating that places the eye on display.

Get behind the steering wheel and experience the most thrilling and interactive race of your gaming career with the video game bumper car steering wheel. This re-purposed bumper car integrates high-tech specs into the retro frame to take racing games to new levels.

Introduce your newborn to the greatest trilogy ever made with the Star Wars baby crib mobile. Featuring miniature aircraft like the X-Wing and Millennium Falcon, your baby will be transported to a galaxy so far, far away that they might actually sleep soundly for once.

Show your guests how twisted you really are with the scary monster lightswitch cover. Whether you’re decorating a mad geneticist’s lab, grossing out your friends, or just getting into the spirit of Halloween, these creepy light switch covers are sure to add a bold look.

Let the piranha coffee mug help you begin your workday with the same aggressive go-get-em attitude they’ll demonstrate upon seeing you enter into their territory.  Hand carved with extreme attention to detail, this coffee mug is ideal for drinking your morning cup of Joe.

Scare your way into the hearts of friends and family by surprising them with the mini chocolate skulls. Available in either milk, dark, or white chocolate, these bite sizes skulls contain a delicious walnut/candy brain and make great treats for the Halloween season.

No gift will satisfy the intellectual handyman quite like the hardware chess set. This custom set features creatively designed pieces made entirely out of various nuts and bolts, all anxiously waiting to strategically fight on the custom painted 8″ x 8″ battleground.

Save the galaxy while simultaneously rewarding your taste buds by licking these savory Death Star lollipops. These hand-made intergalactic lollipops feature a smooth surface and intricate detailing guaranteed to satisfy the sweet tooth of any Star Wars fan.

If you’ve ever wanted to cover yourself in concrete spikes, you finally can when you purchase the spikey vest. This spikey vest is covered in hand-crafted, pastel-toned concrete spikes, and it is guaranteed to make you look like a creature from the blimey deep.

Who says jewelry can’t also be practical? The multi-tool utility ring is the ultimate fashion accessory for the MacGyver-like handyman who likes to always be prepared for any situation. It’s just like having a Swiss army knife on your ring finger.

Don’t let “fear of labels” stop you from being romantic on Valentine’s Day. With the “It’s Complicated” Valentine’s Day card, you can show that <del>special someone</del> friend that you are thinking about them, but it’s totally not a big deal or anything. Whatever.

Turtle power! With these Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles hat no one will ever question why you skateboard through feces infested sewer tunnels or why enjoy showering yourself in green chemical waste. These convertible TMNT hats are also available in multiple colors.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Moon Pillow
content: The moon can be extremely fickle. Luckily, with the glow in the dark moon pillow you’ll be able to enjoy a full moon no matter what the lunar cycle may indicate. Once the lights go off, the life-like image on the pillow begins to emit a soothing glow that lulls you to sleep.

It may be impossible to get your hands on Mario’s magic shrooms but with the Super Mario piranha plant pipe in your hands you’ll be able to soar just as high. This quality pipe features a one-of-a-kind design and double blown Pyrex glass for maximum durability.

Introducing the Yoda hoodie. Half Jedi robe, half Jedi master, and all around awesome. This one of a kind custom made hoodie provides a relaxed, comfortable fit and features an intricately designed hood that will have you looking like the great Yoda.

Declare your undying love to the entire galaxy using the Stars Wars wedding rings. When exchanging vows with your Princess, there’s no better  way to show off your geeky love than by giving each other these tasteful and totally epic silver wedding bands.

Broadcast your love for old school cinema by toting around the audio reel to reel bag. This custom bag features intricate detailing for enhanced authenticity and is made from 100% Spanish wool so it’s lightweight and even water resistant.

Redefine what fine jewelry means with the turntable ring. This unnecessarily gaudy piece of flare will allow you to flaunt your excessive wealth like never before with an 18k gold frame and black diamond turntable guaranteed to get you noticed by all the ladies.

Add a bit of old world mysticism to any room with the ancient ruins terrarium. This hand-carved wonder resembles an artifact you’d find while exploring through the most remote parts of the planet – the stoic stone deity peers into your room, and your soul!

There she blows… your nose. The whale tissue cover can be placed over any existing tissue box in order to add a bit of whimsy to any bathroom decor. During flu season there’s no better companion to have by your side when you come down with a case of the sniffles.

Nothing’s quite as effective as the Gameboy soap bar for removing all the grime and sweat that result after an arduous day of gaming. This awesome soap bar will take you on a nostalgic ride that leaves you feeling and smelling springtime fresh.

Sharks are known for having the ability to devour virtually anything – even dirty laundry – which is why the shark laundry basket makes an awesome addition to any bedroom. Just make sure to watch out for the deadly jaws when dropping in your dirty clothes.

Make your home look a little more seasick with the curvy bookshelf, the bookshelf that makes your living room into a veritable Salvador Dali painting. These bookshelves are handcrafted of hard wood, and will hold your books up straight while giving your eyes a treat.

You might want a steam-powered watch to match your top hat made of gears, but this steampunk watch is going to match your get-up even better. As a bonus, you won’t burn your wrist with steam, and you’ll be able to tell time when you’re cleaning your goggles.

Decorate your library with these unique folded book paper art. With a bold 3D look, these sculptures are crafted by folding the pages from actual books into legible words of your choosing. They make an excellent gift idea for book lovers and librarians.

These gold-plated space invader earrings are laser-etched to look just like the space invaders you used to try and shoot up in the arcades. These little dudes won’t be trying to invade, and you won’t be trying to shoot them — but they will look great on your ears.

Cuddle up with your favorite city symbol, the NYC manhole cover pillow. You might not have thought of the manhole cover as especially cuddly, but this one is fluffy and cushy as well as stylish. And it doesn’t belie a festering sewer full of run-off, so that’s a bonus.

Keep your dice games honest with these precision machined dice. Guaranteed to have a perfect balance in each set, these dice come in a variety of precision machined metals. From aluminum to stainless steel to titanium, these perfectly crafted dice are for serious players.

These unique guitar picks are fashioned out of real quarters featuring none other than the first President of the United States of ‘Murica. George Washington cannot tell a lie, but he can melt your face off when his face is properly attached to set of electric guitar strings.

Experience the displeasure of living in a world of stubborn anger with the grumpy cat hat. Inspired by the grumpy cat internet meme, this handcrafted fleece hat will keep you warm in the cold wintery months, and is sure to get you a few real life upvotes.

Make your bathroom cool again with the skateboard vanity light, the light that makes you yearn for your rebellious kick-flipping days again. Fortunately for you, skating has always been cool, and still is, so this light will look super retro-chic in your apartment.

Immortalize yourself in LEGO form with these personalized LEGO portraits. If you’ve ever wondered what you’d look like in LEGO form, now is your chance to make it a reality as your submitted photo will be beautifully drawn into a LEGO’ized version.

Make your next tea party a little more interesting with sugar cube skulls, the sugar cubes that come in the shape of a dried out human skull. These skull cubes will sweeten your tea, give your guests a fright, and will look lovely next to your grandmother’s china.

The wearable planter necklace allows you to put a bit of greenery into your life, even if you live in a busy city and work in a parking garage. Plant a spring of lavender or lettuce in your necklace, and enjoy a fresh scent or a fresh snack whenever you need one.

Store your books, dvds, and other home paraphernalia on a bookshelf you deserve, but don’t need right now with this Batman bookshelf. With a Nolan Batman series inspired design of the bat symbol, this unique bookshelf is a must have home decor piece.

Charge your devices and give off some warm lighting in your home or office with this clever USB charger outlet lamp. Available in a several different colors, this unique forty watt lamp doubles as a electrical outlet and USB charger station.

Don’t let those delicious White Russians leave water stains on your tables – with The Big Lebowski coaster set you’ll have the Dude and company to protect your furniture from drink sweat. It’s the best coaster money can buy, but that’s just like our opinion, man.

Share something special with your best friend without being cliché – the peanut butter and jelly sandwich necklaces are a cute twist on the heart necklaces broken in half and worn between two good friends. Now all you have to figure out is are you a PB or J person.

After the wild success of the Harry Potter movies, the famous story of wizards and hobbits was turned into a book series which had moderate success. If you happen to be a fan of those books, you can now flaunt your love with these mini Harry Potter book charms.

Start coloring with the full power of the rainbow with these unique 7 colors in 1 rainbow pencils. Truly a pencil like you’ve never seen before, they were crafted out of magical unicorn blessed trees that are found only in the deepest recesses of rainbowland.

Laws are stupid. Updating your twitter every 18 seconds is far more important than driving responsibly on the road. And now with the iCrash steering wheel adapter you can tweet, check your Facebook news feed, and watch movies all at the same time. Smart!

Start your own fellowship with this hand knit Dwarven beard hat. Inspired by Gimli the dwarf warrior from Lord Of The Rings, this incredibly detailed fleece helm has a detachable beard, and for just three easy payments of $99.99 you can upgrade it to mithril!

Keep your braaaaaaiinnsss nice and warm with this cartoon zombie beanie. Hand knit from acrylic yarn, the zombie beanie looks like its gnawing down as your tasty cranium, and with its availability in multiple head sizes, it’s a great gift idea for zombie lovers of all ages.

Show off your iPhone’s darker side with the steampunk iPhone dock. Complete with gears and aged metalwork, the dock will charge your phone and connect it to the vintage earpiece. Stop lamenting how modern your phone looks — steampunk it!

Add some zombie flair to your library with these zombie hand bookmarks. With zombie hands in your favorite book, you’ll never feel alone again. Ditch those boring kitten bookmarks and stick a pair of zombie hands in your first edition of World War Z.

Nintendo Cartridge earrings are the accessory that lets your mates know that you’re a child of the 80s and 90s. These earrings, in the exact shape of cartridges featuring Super Mario Brothers 2 and 3, are each less than an inch wide.

Add some unique eco-friendly lighting to your home with this recycled camera owl lamp. This wise looking owl lamp features a variety of recycled camera parts to give it a quirky and lovable design that is guaranteed to be your favorite lamp in your home.

If AK-47s are too bold for your liking, why not scale down to some lovely pistol lamps? These handmade 9mm pistol lamps are cast in ceramic plaster molds and come complete with the black shades – making these pistol lamps an excellent lighting fixture for a gun nut’s home.

Read your children a bedtime story like never before with this clever bedtime story blanket. Ideal for the lover of good books, the bedtime story blanket features a few pages of literature for you to read as you cuddle up and get ready for a good night’s rest.

The only 100% way to ensure your teens never catch bed bugs is to never let them have sleep. But with rap music and that satanic music television sending subliminal messages, the most realistic approach to keeping them safe is to give them these condom pillows.

No true Trekkie’s home should be without this amazing Starship Enterprise coffee table. Handcrafted by wood artist Barry Shields, this Enterprise ship features beautifully crafted lines using a combination of cherry, ash, and poplar wood. You’ll never get laid again, guaranteed!

Give that special someone a heart necklace that they won’t find cliche and cheesy with this pixelated heart necklace. Able to be broken in half – perhaps symbolically – the pixelated heart necklace is an excellent gift idea for geeky jewelery collectors.

Decorate your bathroom with the greatest plumber you’ll ever know with the Super Mario Bros toilet seat. This hand painted toilet seat depicts the classic Super Mario tearing it up in the nostalgic 1-1 level, and comes triple layered in polyurethane to protect the paint.

Have the friendliest ghost in New York City hang out in your home with this Ghostbusters Slimer sculpture. This incredibly detailed Slimer sculpture is made from a strong silicone rubber, and when hung on your wall it gives the appearance that he is bursting out!

You’re more than just a wizard, Harry – you’re a fashionista! With these clever Harry Potter glasses rings you can look good while showing off your geeky Potter side. Available in three bold colors, the Harry Potter glasses rings are a great gift idea for Harry Potter fans.

Give yourself some direction in life by adding the nautical compass wall decal to your home. With its ability to always point you in the right direction, the nautical compass wall decal will give you a truly centered feeling in your own home.

Don’t cower in fear of the Empire – now you can be prepared to defend yourself against stormtroopers, Boba Fett, or even Darth Vader with these collectible Star Wars villains targets. These geeky silhouette targets/posters are the perfect gift idea for the vigilant Rebel.

Fans of the Legend of Zelda will find these eight-bit earrings to be the perfect accessory. Honor the legendary video game with earrings designed to look exactly like the original little Link for the NES. You’ll be the coolest fangirl in Hyrule.

Enchant your fingers with these lovely octopus rings. Available in either sterling, yellow gold, or black powder coated, these octopus rings make an excellent gift idea for the collector of unique jewelry and those intrigued by the captivating cephalopod.

You might be broke in the real world, but you can be rich in the land of Hyrule with these over-sized Zelda rupee pillows. You won’t need to chop down any grass or smash any local vendor jars to get your hands on these colorful rupees, all you need is your credit card!

The groom almost got away, but the zombie bridge always get her prey! These zombie bride wedding cake toppers are perfect for a zombie lover’s wedding, foreshadowing the boring zombie like life you’ll soon have once you get married.

Glorify your home with the shining light that only Iron Man can bestow upon you with this unbelievable Iron Man stained glass. Featuring 334 pieces of glass, this incredibly detailed Iron Man stained glass is a true collector’s piece for any geek.

This is the Droid you’ve been looking for – the R2-D2 baby costume is perfect for baby geeks, offering a Star Wars themed onesie and a matching hat. It’s also available in a gown style, as well as a toddler sized version, so you can decorate your offspring for years to come.

Go all out at your next DJ gig with this replica Deadmau5 LED helmet. This fully functional Deadmau5 helmet contains 168 programmable LEDs so you create any type animation style desired or even have it react to the music that is playing.

Give your light switches at home a creative twist with these kooky toggle light switches. These fully functional light switches use gears and leverage to turn on and off your lights, and are a perfect gift idea for an engineer’s home or office.

Harness the raw power of a rainbow farting Pop Tart cat flying through outer space with this Nyan Cat necklace. Perfect for youtube geeks and internet meme collectors, the Nyan Cat necklace is a handmade clay piece, so each necklace is unique.

Stop dressing up in lame cliche costumes every Halloween – this year you can go as the scariest dinosaur ever with this life size baby T-Rex costume! Though your legs might be visible during day time, at night this incredibly realistic T-Rex costume will fool everyone!

Add some nostalgic decor to your home with this melted Army men bowl. This clever bowl features three different colored Army men of various poses, melted down into a functional yet decorative storage bowl that will be an instant conversation piece in any home.

Just when you thought it was safe to go back into the water with a ukulele – the great white king of the seas returns. This Jaws shark attack ukulele is a custom built maple instrument that will strike fear into the hearts of your former band mates who replaced you with a guitarist.

Dogs and mailmen might hate each other, but now you can help bridge their differences with this Beagle dog mailbox. This adorable doggy mailbox is shaped and painted like a Beagle, and is a perfect gift idea to personalize a dog lover’s home.

Give your home library an industrial feel to it with this plumbing pipes bookshelf. Using real industrial pipes, this unique bookshelf will give your home a rugged yet modern look and will provide storage space in even the tightest of spaces.

Give your child a cute and original costume this Halloween with the eggs and bacon kid’s costume. Featuring a tasty bacon hat and a sunny side up torso, these adorable fleece costumes will make your kid look so cute you’ll want to just eat him/her up, literally.

For the first time ever you can own a Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles ooze canister and transform your boring pet turtles into pizza eating crime fighters! These replica Ninja Turtle ooze canisters are made from real glass and metal, and are great for TMNT fans.

Do you love bacon so much that you’d wear it as clothing? Well now you can do just that without the weird looks and attacks from hungry animals with the bacon tie. This delicious looking bacon tie is hand painted and will clog your arteries with style!

Enhance your pathetic skin and bones with impressive metal with these mechanical hands. Perfect for mad scientists, street fighters, and people who dream of replacing their bone with metal, these fully functional mechanical hands will make you a force to be reckoned with.

Show off your vast riches while staying comfy with these hundred dollar stack pillows. At sixty five dollars each, these unique dollar stacks pillows have a respectable US dollar to comfy pillow conversion rate, and are perfect for flaunting your riches off to guests.

Give a mind blowing performance to the entire Mushroom Kingdom and turn yourself into a Princess Peach panty dropper with this Super Mario guitar. These custom made, hand crafted, and air brushed Super Mario themed guitars are perfect for the geeky musician.

Keep your hands feeling fresh by washing them with severed fingers! These creepy yet realistic looking human fingers are actually mini soap bars with a wonderful watermelon scent added to them. These severed fingers soap bars go great with serial killer wallpaper, too!

Despite the best efforts of the DEA, the purest form of crystal meth available – known as the blue stuff – can now be purchased on the web. This crystal meth rock candy is perfect for fans of Breaking Bad, or just as a gag gift for hard drug addicts.

Make your kid look like a creative soldier of fortune with this crayon ammo bandolier. Perfect for carrying around a large selection of crayons, this nifty crayon bandolier comes in a variety of colors and will ensure your child never gets beat up in school.

Show off your geeky side with these mini video game controller rings. Available in XBox360, PS3, and even Nintendo Wii style, as well as in a variety of colors, these mini video game controller rings are the perfect gift idea for that special gamer in your life.

It’s no secret that vampires need blood to survive – but they’ve taken their blood lust to a new level with these sexy vampire menstrual pads. Designed to take advantage of the Twilight / romantic vampire craze, these pads can keep a vampire fed for an entire week!

Frolic around looking like a deer with this deer antler hat knitting pattern. You’ve struggled for years to grow antlers on your own, and despite your best efforts of trying to will yourself to evolve your cranium, your best bet is to knit yourself some antlers with this knitting pattern.

Jesus saves in many ways – but not many people know that he is quite the frugal penny pincher. With the Jesus saves piggy bank you can do the Lord’s work by saving all the loose change you find, bringing you one step closer to living like the holiest of holy.

Clean yourself with the power of the dark side with this giant Darth Vader soap bar. Weighing in at over two pounds, the giant Darth Vader soap bar is an easy way to get your <del>dumb kids</del> young padawans to wash their hands before dinner, but also makes a nice decorative piece.

Give your home bar an apt lighting system with these beer can track lights. Available in a variety of beer can styles, these unique track lights will transform your bar area from a dingy alcoholic’s sulking spot to a fun and lively party zone where everyone will want to go!

Relax in a bean bag of deliciousness with this baked potato bean bag. Featuring a hand dyed brown exterior and a butter shaped satin pillow for added comfort, the baked potato bean bag will be the most comfortable side dish you will ever lay down in.

A must have collector’s item for any fan of Alice in Wonderland, the iconic caterpillar has been painstakingly recreated with this felt sculpture that even includes the hookah smoking pipe and comes packaged with his leather signature patch and certificate of authenticity.

You might not own a hovering speeder bike, but you can still look like an intimidating storm trooper on your motorcycle with this leather stormtrooper riding mask. This steampunk style rider’s mask is hand made and can be safely worn at speeds up to 85 miles per hour.

Turn your mailbox into a groovy love machine with these VW Bus mailboxes. Available in a variety of psychedelic colors, these functional and handmade steel VW Bus mailboxes are perfect for expressing your individuality to all your neighbors and your mailman.

Win the heart of that special geek with these geeky romantic cards. Available individually or as a pack of five, these geeky romantic cards range from Zelda to Duck Hunt to Super Mario themes and will instantly make an old school gamer fall in love with you.

There’s a bomb in the house, and it smells amazing! Now with these clever dynamite stick incense holders you can burn incense sticks while freaking out your family. The incense stick will look like a wick burning away, ready to ignite the dynamite.

Now you can cast some disturbing shadows on your walls with these zombie shadow casters. Perfect for zombie themed parties, simply place these mini mahogany zombies in front of a small candle and a realistic zombie silhouette will appear behind it.

Own a pair of shoes that are out of this world with these hand painted and custom made galaxy shoes. Simply specify your shoe size, and your shoes will be painted in the awe inspiring style you see before you, or you can even request a different cosmic color scheme.

Walk tall and carry a big sword with this massive Devil May Cry inspired sword. This giant steel sword is both an artistic collector’s piece that would look great hanging on any wall, and a functional piece of weaponry that will dish out some serious destruction.

Add a pixelated stairway anywhere in your home with this 8-Bit secret stairway. Inspired by the retro art design of 8-Bit video games such as The Legend of Zelda, this clever floor decal is available in either Desert Sand or Dungeon Blue colors.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Moon Sticker
content: Add some lunar ambiance to your home with this giant glow in the dark moon sticker. Also available in smaller sizes, these glowing moon stickers are perfect for a kids room or just a neat hangout spot, giving you a beautiful display of art and science.

Give your dog some style with these assorted silly dog hats. With everything from viking hats to birthday cake hats, these hilarious dog hats will keep scruffums warm during the cold winter months while also giving him a stylish look that will surely be a conversation starter.

Now you can store your computer data on an external hard drive encased in the cartridge of arguably the greatest game ever made – the Legend of Zelda. Available in 500GB, 750GB, and 1TB versions, these Zelda cartridge hard drives are the ultimate geeky PC accessory.

Tired of being treated amazingly by strangers because of your dashing good looks? Want to experience the world while being treated like a disgusting slob? Well now you can with the permanently sweaty shirt that comes with sweat and pit stains that will never come off.

Show off your artistic side with this iPhone case that looks like a painter’s set of watercolors. These hand made iPhone cases are available in three different case colors and are a perfect gift idea for painters or people with a creative side in general.

Release the Kraken! Now you can smoke out of a beautifully crafted glass pipe shaped like a monstrous octopus. This functional piece of art measures just over seven inches in length, and come in a variety of colors – even glow in the dark versions!

Make yourself look like an evil genius with a brain so potent that it cannot be contained in a puny mortal skull! This knitted brain beanie is perfect for showing off your superior cranium, and will definitely be a conversation starter when worn.

Combine all the elements of strategy into one cute necklace with the rock paper scissors necklace. These hand made necklaces are crafted using a gold plated scissor charm, a torn piece of a novel’s page, and a small rock found from the shore of Lake Michigan.

Drop the subtleties of secret handshakes and catchphrases to identify yourself as a fellow Redditor – the Reddit alien hat will instantly make you identifiable as an intelligent and informed websurfer who also has a debilitating weakness for pictures of cats.

Style your home in retro geek style with the Pac-Man ottoman. Made from acrylic upholstery, these Pac-Man ottomans come in a variety of color combinations and are perfect for an arcade room or geeky lounge area. Not recommended for houses haunted by ghosts.

Drink from a coffee mug with attitude – the spikey coffee mug is a handmade cup that takes no prisoners and lives by its own rules. Available in a variety of colors, these spikey coffee mugs are perfect for adding a little toughness to your morning cup of joe.

Crown yourself as the Queen with these solid fourteen carat gold crown rings. Made to order with custom ring sizes, the crown ring will fit perfectly on your royal fingers, or makes a great gift idea for people who always dreamed of being a highborn.

You’ve researched your target, prepared the room so as to not leave any evidence, and now you can perform your morning ritual of being a cereal killer with this clever spoon. The cereal killer spoon is a hand stamped vintage spoon, and makes a great gift for heavy cereal eaters.

Carry and protect your baby ninja turtle style with this turtle shell baby harness. The turtle shell is an attachment for the baby bjorn harness, and will give your newborn baby the confidence that the hardened shell of a turtle has got his back – literally.

Be the center of attention all night long with this head turning disco ball dress. Whether you’ve got Saturday night fever or just love flashy apparel, the disco ball dress will instantly become your favorite little outfit for painting the town red.

Look like a true hero with this epic hand crafted leather dragon slayer armor. Even if you aren’t a dragonborn, you can still look like an epic warlord with this armor. Each piece of the dragon slayer armor set is made to order using 7/8 ounce leather.

Geek up your home with these retro Pac-Man style ghost bookshelves. Perfect for storing books, displaying pictures, and even scaring off interested dates you bring back home, these pixelated Pac-Man ghosts are a must have home accessory for grew up on the game.

Accordions might not have the mainstream appeal that an instrument like a guitar has, but these full size accordion pillows will surely be a favorite in any home. These accordion pillows are capable of compressing and expanding just like the real instrument.

Commit to that special someone like a true geek with these Star Trek engagement rings. With a sterling silver Trekkie insignia design, these engagement rings are perfect for the couple who wish to love and honor each other and live long and prosper.

When the narwhal isn’t baconing at midnight, he’s lounging around in absolute comfort. Now you can share that comfy feeling with these fancy narwhal plushies. Featuring a mustache and monocle, the fancy narwhal plushie exudes class and makes a great snuggle buddy.

Was your home built on an Indian burial ground? Have ghosts been whispering to you instructions to murder your family? If so, you’ve got a ghost infestation problem. Buy yourself a Ghostbusters proton backpack and take care of those pesky apparitions once and for all.

Light up the night in TRON like style with these neon light up sneakers. These handmade light up sneakers use an on board circuitry and an included battery source to create a stunning neon effect at night time, perfect for turning heads at the club or rave.

Be prepared for whatever the land of <del>Hyrule</del> suburbia might throw at you with these Zelda inspired bomb bags. A perfect collector’s item for Zelda gamers, with three soft throw-able yarn bombs included you’ll easily keep the bad guys at bay.

Electrify your audience with beautiful displays of color with these double rainbow hula hoops. With super bright LEDs, these rechargeable rainbow hula hoops are a fun twist on a classic toy and can even be customized with own your choice of LED colors.

Experience earception with these earrings that look like mini ears that have earrings! With a disturbing yet realistic design, these mini ear shaped earrings are hand made and make a great gift idea for people who love strange jewelry.

Slice and dice ingredients for your next meal with this geeky 8-bit Super Mario cutting board. These custom made 8-bit cutting boards are extremely durable and hand finished pixelated masterpieces, and are available in other styles such as Space Invaders.

It’s a trap! These functional bear trap necklaces aren’t for casual jewelry fashionistas – they open and close like a real bear trap with sharp teeth. Available in sterling silver or oxidized black, these clever necklaces make great gifts for outdoorsy types.

It may not bend space and time, but this Doctor Who inspired Tardis bag works great as a carry all for your gear. Constructed using a thick blue felt, the Tardis bag is finely made with an adjustable zipper, adjustable straps, and built in pockets for organized storage.

What should you wear to that wine tasting party? How about a hand made wool vine of grapes necklace! Perfect for wine lovers, this unique and eco-friendly necklace will be an instant conversation starter and also can be ordered with the matching grape earrings.

Show off your destructive side by wearing one of these mini wrecking ball necklaces. You’ll feel the weight of the solid brass wrecking ball swing as you move about, striking terror in the eyes of your fellow man as the unstoppable momentum builds on the ball.

Warm your home without literally warming your home with these 8-bit fireplace art pieces that are reminscent of the pixelated fires you would see in the Legend of Zelda games. Available in various sizes for different fireplace styles, these geeky fireplaces great for retro gamers.

If you love that classic style of 1950s pin-up girls, these swinging girl necklaces will be a perfect addition to your jewelry collection. Hand cut and soldered, these quaint necklaces come with a seventeen inch sterling silver chain and make a perfect gift for pin-up girl fans.

Barbequing is serious business, and you need a serious grill if you want to be called the grill master. Now you can strike fear in the hearts of salad eaters at the Sunday BBQ with this pistol BBQ grill, and use gun powder to give extra flavor on your steaks, ribs, and chicken.

Turn your chairs into puzzle pieces with these unique jigsaw puzzle chairs that interlock with each other. Available in a variety of colors, the top seat piece of each chair is adjustable, so you can literally rearrange the pieces like you would a real puzzle.

Finish off your wedding cake with an honest touch with these video game addict wedding cake toppers. Available with everything from Starcraft to Call of Duty, these cake toppers are the perfect way to mark the end of his all night gaming sessions and the start of marriage.

Light up your bedroom with a recycled vintage camera that has been masterfully converted into a nightlight. These vintage camera night lights use standard bulbs and even have a sensor that turns them on automatically when the room gets dark at night time.

Add some artistic and unusual lighting to your home with these drippy faucet night lights. Created using real plumbing supplies, turning the valve acts as a light switch for the night light – lefty loosey to turn it on, right tighty to turn it off.

Make yourself look harder, better, faster, and stronger with these replica Daft Punk helmets. These one size fits all helmets include four bright LEDs, an adjustable computer chip for light speeds, and a sealed gold finish for that authentic look.

Use the force to rock out like a true geek with this Star Wars Millennium Falcon guitar! With real working lights and sound effects and a tribute to R2-D2 at the headstock, this playable electric guitar is unquestionably the holy grail of geeky guitars.

Light up your home in a unique and eco-friendly manner – these recycled mini light bulbs are actually oil lamps. Each oil lamp includes a hand made wooden base with a satin finish, and come with easy to install cotton wicks and instructions.

You’re not losing your mind – these incredibly detailed objects that look like edible foods are in fact bars of soap! With everything from Oreos to gummy bears to choose from, these hand made food shaped soap bars not only look great, but they smell great too.

Hyrule is a dangerous place to venture alone – take these house keys! Easy to mount while not causing any damage to your walls, these nostalgic key hangers are a must have household item for old school Legend of Zelda fans.

Load up on your stars and magic mushrooms, because the enemies of the Mario universe have begun their assault on the real world. These Super Mario style chain chomp earrings look like your ears are being nom’ed on by the chain chomps from the Koopa Troop.

The word “useless” gets thrown around a lot on ThisIsWhyImBroke – but these Fine China Brass Knuckles take the cake. Made from real recycled fine China dinnerware, these ironic brass knuckles are perfect for the girl who loves eco-friendly and useless jewelry.

People keep telling you to get a life, but now you can finally show them that they’re idiots – you’re already at full health with these geeky life bar necklaces that also glows in the dark! Inspired by retro video games life bar displays, these necklaces are perfect for a stylish geek.

Want a coffee table that doubles as a fully functional Nintendo controller? This giant hand crafted Nintendo controller coffee table is made from mahogany, and includes a removeable glass top when you want to use it as a gaming controller.

Enjoy the touch and feel of an antique typewriter while still having the modern features of a keyboard and computer with these USB typewriters. Available in a variety of different styles, these modified type writers are truly a hipster’s wet dream.

Own a tiny piece of arcade gaming history with these collectible mini arcade machines. From Street Fighter to Mortal Kombat, each one of these incredibly detailed mini arcades will remind you of your glory days in the arcades, before the era of console gaming.

Throw out those lame family portraits and invest in these custom made zombie paintings. These personalized zombie portraits are hand painted using a photo of you as inspiration, giving you a unique insight into what you’d look like in zombie form.

titleEN: You Are Not The Father Card
content: Few words in the language of men bring greater joy than “you are not the father”. For years, Maury Povich has been delivering this life saving announcement to potential dead beat dads on his talk show, but now you too can deliver the great news with these cards!

Geek out in total comfort with this cleverly designed set of Star Trek pillows. This complete set of geeky throw pillows includes the gold command pillow, blue science pillow, and red engineering pillow – or you can order each pillow individually.

Keep your head warm while looking like a classic gaming icon with the Mega Man hat. This full size replica Mega man helmet is made from a comfortable fleece material, giving you bold looks and insulation during the cold winters your geeky heart desires.

Ever wonder what Beavis and Butthead would look like in real life? These life like sculptures were designed by special effects makeup artist Kevin Kirkpatrick for an art show he was attending, creating a realistic non-cartoon form of the famous characters.

Embrace the inevitable zombie apocalypse with the Zombie Attack Bed Covers. This gory bed set includes a blanket cover and two pillow cases that are screen printed and hand painted with zombie arms, and an ample spread of blood throughout.

Now you can give someone special your heart without ripping out your own literal heart. These life like human hearts are amazingly made entirely from felt, so not only are they awesome to look at, but they are also soft and cuddly.

Live long and prosper in style with these Star Trek Vulcan Beanies with attached ear covers. These incredibly geeky Vulcan hats will keep your head warm while also turning you into an enlightened, emotionless, and perfectly logical being. Kid’s sizes are also available.

When the Discovery Channel announced it would begin replacing Shark Week with Narwhal Week, an all out war erupted between sharks and narwhals. Still yet to be caught on film, this painting is a rare glimpse into one of the many epic battles being waged right now.

Power up your collection of footwear with these hand painted Super Mario high top sneakers that feature all the classics from the Super Mario series – from goombas to pirahna plants to power stars to Bowser himself – these will be the most nostalgic shoes you’ll ever own.

Keep your drink insulated and your hands dry with this cute monster shark drink cozy. Hand knit from machine washable acrylic, these shark drink cozies come in a variety of colors and make a great gift for a Shark Week themed drinking party!

Recycling and steampunk will never look better than they do on this Optimus Prime statue. Standing nearly nine feet tall and weighing in at over a thousand pounds, this steampunk Optimus Prime statue is an incredible art piece for both geeks and steampunks enthusiasts.

Keep track of your progress while reading your favorite book with these clever Wicked Witch Bookmarks. Made from polymer clay and thick cardboard, the feet of the wicked witch will stick out over two inches so you’ll easily be able open to the page you were last on.

If you want to stay looking trendy on those long space travels, nothing tops these Princess Leia headphones. Designed to fit comfortably over your royal ears, these Princess Leia style buns also work great in the winter as earmuffs. May the Schwartz be with you.

Are you feeling lucky today, punk? The .44 magnum is one of the most powerful handguns in the world, capable of blowing your head clean off – and now it’s the manliest ring in the world. This ring makes a great gift for guns enthusiasts, and Dirty Harry impressionists.

Have a geeky jam session with this Pac-Man shaped ukulele. This fully functional ukulele is made out of maple with an ipa fretboard. These ukuleles are also available in various styles such as Steampunk, Transformers, Cupcake, and Panda style via Celetano’s shop.

Looking for a cute way to show off your inner pyscho? Then you should try the chainsaw necklace charm – this unique hand made silver necklace charm is a great gift idea for people who love unusual and interesting jewelry and comes with the necklace chain too.

It’s dangerous to go alone, take this Zelda Master Sword USB Drive! This Zelda Sword unsheathes to reveal the USB drive, comes in various memory sizes from 4 GB all the way up to 32 GB, and makes a great gift idea for Zelda fans.

Roll out looking like a true Autobot with this Steampunk Optimus Prime Helmet. This highly detailed, battle worn, bronze finished Optimus Prime helmet is a full size adult costume helmet but also makes a great display piece for any geeky room.

Looking to decorate your home with something intense? Try the steampunk predator statue – this giant statue stands over eight feet tall and weighs over half a ton! Made from recycled metals, this Predator statue will easily be the greatest thing you ever own.

If you love narwhals, these handmade clay narwhal figurines will be your kryptonite. Each little narwhal figurine is just under five inches long when including the size of it’s horn, and because they are hand made figurines no one narwhal is alike.

Live your life on the edge by washing your hands with grenades! These hand grenade soap bars are custom made to look like the standard issue World War II style steel body hand grenade and make a cool house warming gift for military families.

Our spidey sense is tingling – it’s saying we’re about to go broke thanks to this unbelievable Metal Spiderman Table from the amazing Kreatworks Etsy shop that specializes in huge metallic statues. This Spiderman Table is a definite must buy for Spiderman fans.

Go to war with these Warhammer Nerf Guns – available in both pistol and rifle form. These Warhammer fire arms are fully functional hand painted modified Nerf guns with incredible detail and make a cool gift idea for Warhammer fans.

Show off your geeky side with these piranha plant earrings. These hand made earrings are modeled after the always troublesome piranha plants from the Super Mario games, and have a clever design where it looks like the plant is biting on your ears.

Protect your precious computer files with the Zelda Hylian Shield USB thumb drive. This custom made Zelda Hlian USB thumb drive is handmade and comes in multiple gigabyte sizes and makes a great gift for geeks, gamers, and Zelda fans alike.

If you want to classy up your home office then look no further than the Steampunk computer monitor and keyboard. This Steampunk themed monitor and keyboard combo perfectly captures the artistic styles of the Victorian era and makes a cool gift idea for Steampunk fans.

Fight off evil blood suckers with this Vampire Hunting Kit. The kit includes everything you’ll need to kill a vampire such as but not limited to: a cross sharpened into a dagger, vintage coffin nails, vintage holy bible, and all the other essentials to kill a vampire.

These bold Russian style AK-47 lamps can be powered by electricity or vodka and make a great gift for thugs, gangsters, goons, and mobsters alike. Each AK-47 lamp is hand made with extra attention to detail and stand nearly three feet tall.

These are the droids you’re looking for… The R2-D2 Beanie is a hand knitted head warmer styled after one of the most easily recognized Star Wars characters and is a cool gift for Star Wars geeks. Quantity is limited on these R2-D2 Beanies so act fast.

From the depths of the murky sea arises this massive tentacle candle holder. Created with influences from classic tales of sea monsters, the Tentacle Candle Holder is a very unique way to display your candles in your home.

Sweet Jesus, rage face and internet meme paintings? Ah Yeahhhhhhh, this will go great in the bachelor frog pad, but fffffffuuuuuuuuuuuu this is going to break the bank! These Internet Meme Paintings are the perfect gift for the Reddit gift exchange.

In the year 2053 Nerf technology has become the dominant form of handgun ammunition. This Steampunk styled Nerf handgun is painted by hand to give it that amazing steampunk look and feel, and also includes six Nerf darts.

These hand made finger puppets wonderfully capture the essence of Bob Ross, the amazing man who taught us the joy of painting. With these finger puppets, you can keep Bob Ross’ legacy going by teaching a younger generation the joy of painting.

What you’re looking at isn’t a real playstation controller, it’s a bar of soap! This playstation controller soap bar is “grape soda” scented and is made with high quality soap ingredients and is a great gift idea for the hygienically forgetful gamer.

Show your undying love with bow knot rings available in all sizes and in both gold and sterling silver. This romantic gift is an thoughtful ring to give someone who you want to remind that you always love them, especially as a gift for valentines or an anniversary.

Floppy disks are no longer obsolete relics of technology past, because now they are cute and comfy little sleeping buddies. Made from 100% cotton, these 16″ by 16″ geeky pillows come loaded with personality and will add a personal touch to any room.

Looking to attract gamer nerds with reckless abandon? These video game inspired health and mana potion earrings will score huge points with the geeky fellas, so you’ll be able to choose from an endless amount of interested guys who have no idea how to please you.

Personalize your pillows with these four custom made scrabble pillows. You can also order multiple pillows to combine for one giant word, such as Pseudopseudohypoparathyroidism, or stick with the standard four pillows with your choice of letters.

The Baby Yoda Beanie is the only way to keep your baby warm and ensure he or she will grow up with a high connection to The Force. The Baby Yoda Beanie is a hand knitted green beanie that has fabric stiffeners to ensure the Yoda ears will stay lifted.
